20The%20manner%20of%20death%20is%20accident.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKetamine%20is%20illegally%20used%20as%20a%20recreational%20drug%20for%20its%20numbing%20and%20hallucinogenic%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drug%20can%20also%20be%20used%20by%20doctors%20as%20an%20anesthetic%2C%20and%20researchers%20are%20exploring%20its%20use%20as%20a%20mental%20health%20treatment.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerry%20wrote%20in%20his%20memoirs%20of%20how%20he%20had%20relied%20on%20using%20ketamine%20daily%20at%20points%20during%20his%20battles%20with%20addiction.%20He%20said%20the%20drug%20eased%20his%20pain%20and%20helped%20with%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHas%20my%20name%20written%20all%20over%20it%20--%20they%20might%20as%20well%20have%20called%20it%20'Matty%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20of%20ketamine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaking%20K%20is%20like%20being%20hit%20in%20the%20head%20with%20a%20giant%20happy%20shovel.%20But%20the%20hangover%20was%20rough%20and%20outweighed%20the%20shovel%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20Perry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'The%20Big%20Terrible%20Thing'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFriends%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20followed%20the%20lives%20of%20six%20New%20Yorkers%20navigating%20adulthood%2C%20dating%20and%20careers%2C%20drew%20a%20massive%20global%20following.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20as%20he%20delivered%20on-air%20gag%20after%20gag%20--%20and%20earned%20a%20fortune%20--%20Perry%20was%20struggling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20attended%20multiple%20rehabilitation%20clinics%20to%20combat%20addiction%20to%20painkillers%20and%20alcohol.%20In%202018%20he%20suffered%20a%20burst%20colon%2C%20related%20to%20drug%20usage%2C%20and%20underwent%20multiple%20surgeries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20memoir%20%26quot%3BFriends%2C%20Lovers%20and%20the%20Big%20Terrible%20Thing%2C%26quot%3B%20published%20last%20year%2C%20Perry%20described%20going%20through%20detox%20dozens%20of%20times.%20He%20dedicated%20the%20book%20to%20%26quot%3Ball%20of%20the%20sufferers%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20wrote%20in%20the%20prologue%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20should%20be%20dead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20mostly%20been%20sober%20since%202001%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3Bsave%20for%20about%20sixty%20or%20seventy%20little%20mishaps%20over%20the%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20examiner's%20report%20does%20not%20specify%20how%20or%20when%20Perry%20had%20consumed%20the%20fatal%20dose%20of%20ketamine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20found%20that%20trace%20amounts%20were%20detected%20in%20his%20stomach%2C%20and%20that%20prescription%20medications%20and%20loose%20pills%20were%20present%20at%20his%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerry%20was%20undergoing%20medical%20treatment%20involving%20ketamine%20--%20but%20his%20most%20recent%20known%20infusion%20was%20more%20than%20a%20week%20before%20his%20death%2C%20meaning%20that%20dose%20would%20no%20longer%20have%20been%20in%20his%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20examiner's%20report%20says%20the%20levels%20of%20ketamine%20in%20Perry's%20blood%20were%20comparable%20to%20higher-range%20levels%20used%20as%20general%20anesthetic%20in%20surgeries%2C%20and%20would%20cause%20overstimulation%20of%20the%20heart%20and%20problems%20breathing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20could%20have%20caused%20Perry%20to%20lapse%20into%20unconsciousness%2C%20with%20drowning%20then%20becoming%20a%20contributory%20cause%20of%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerry's%20coronary%20artery%20disease%2C%20and%20his%20use%20of%20buprenorphine%20to%20treat%20severe%20pain%2C%20would%20have%20made%20him%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20effects%20of%20ketamine%2C%20the%20report%20finds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20alcohol%20was%20detected%20in%20his%20system%20by%20the%20autopsy%20report.%20Nor%20were%20there%20any%20traces%20of%20other%20drugs%20such%20as%20cocaine%2C%20heroin%20or%20fentanyl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'The%206%20of%20us