%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupplements-for-sex-libido-erectile-dysfunction-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Matthew%20Perry%20died%20from%20'acute%20effects%20of%20ketamine'%20and%20drowning%2C%20toxicology%20report%20finds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Matthew%20Perry.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653e469f356802a56be6e114%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222824%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMatthew%20Perry.%3Cp%3EAxelle%2FBauer-Griffin%2FFilmMagic%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMatthew%20Perry's%20death%20was%20caused%20by%20drowning%20and%20ketamine%2C%20the%20LA%20County%20coroner%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%2054-year-old%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20a%20hot%20tub%20at%20his%20Los%20Angeles%20home%20in%20October.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20manner%20of%20the%C2%A0%26quot%3BFriends%26quot%3B%20actor's%20death%20was%20ruled%20an%20accident%2C%20according%20to%20the%20coroner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmatthew-perry-dead-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMatthew%20Perry's%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20ruled%20an%20accident%2C%20with%20the%20cause%20being%20the%20effects%20of%20ketamine%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20County%20Coroner's%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20County%20of%20Los%20Angeles%20Department%20of%20Medical%20Examiner%20(DME)%20determined%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20for%2054-year-old%20actor%20Matthew%20Langford%20Perry%20as%20the%20acute%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fketamine-drug-depression-antidepressant-effects-special-k-clubbing-medicine-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeffects%20of%20ketamine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20County%20Corner's%20Office%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20Frida