n%20it%20by%20fraud%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20not%20conspiracy%20theories%20these%20are%20facts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20regret%20a%20damn%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Giuliani%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20first%20jury%20verdict%20in%20a%20defamation%20trial%20over%20Trump%20election%20lies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20earlier%2C%20much%20larger%20lawsuit%20from%20Dominion%20Voting%20Systems%20against%20Fox%20News%20went%20through%20the%20jury%20selection%20process%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffox-news-settles-dominion-defamation-lawsuit-trial-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esettled%20at%20the%20eleventh%20hour%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20right-wing%20media%20network%20agreeing%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdominion-fox-news-settlement-takeaways-what-happens-next-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epay%20%24787.5%20million%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20other%20cases%20%E2%80%94%20including%20ones%20against%20farther-right%20media%20organizations%20One%20America%20News%20and%20Newsmax%20%E2%80%94%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foan-settles-dominion-executive-eric-coomer-defamation-lawsuit-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealso%20settled%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feveryone-dominion-smartmatic-suing-defamation-election-conspiracy-theories-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eothers%20are%20hurtling%20toward%20their%20own%20trials%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20is%20the%20trial%20against%20Giuliani%2C%20held%20in%20federal%20court%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%2C%20that%20perhaps%20best%20exemplifies%20both%20the%20personal%20harms%20of%20election%20conspiracy%20theories%20and%20just%20how%20starkly%20the%20theories%20cut%20against%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20case%20is%20unprecedented%2C%26quot%3B%20plaintiff%20lawyer%20Michael%20Gottlieb%20said%20in%20his%20closing%20argument.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20the%20lies%20in%20this%20case%20became%20part%20of%20a%20sustained%20campaign%20%E2%80%94%20the%20purpose%20of%20which%20was%20to%20overturn%20the%20election%20%E2%80%94%20which%20had%20the%20collateral%20effect%20of%20these%20lies%20that%20rocketed%20around%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20interviews%20and%20on%20his%20social%20media%20accounts%2C%20Giuliani%2C%20then%20a%20personal%20attorney%20for%20Trump%2C%20pushed%20the%20false%20claim%20that%20Freeman%20and%20Moss%20had%20produced%20%26quot%3Bsuitcases%26quot%3B%20full%20of%20fake%20ballots%20from%20under%20a%20table%20and%20included%20them%20in%20the%20vote%20count%20while%20working%20as%20election%20employees%20in%20Atlanta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20cited%20a%20grainy%2C%20edited%20clip%20of%20security%20footage%20that%20was%20posted%20online%20by%20Trump's%20campaign%20and%20that%2C%20in%20reality%2C%20did%20not%20show%20any%20such%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiuliani%20falsely%20claimed%20%E2%80%94%20even%20after%20Georgia%20election%20officials%20said%20the%20allegations%20were%20false%20%E2%80%94%20that%20the%20video%20showed%20Freeman%20and%20Moss%20pulling%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%20ballots%20while%20Republican%20election%20observers%20weren't%20looking%2C%20that%20they%20illegally%20counted%20some%20ballots%20multiple%20times%2C%20and%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Bpassing%20around%20USB%20ports%20as%20if%20they're%20vials%20of%20heroin%20or%20cocaine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20all%20evidence%2C%20Giuliani%20said%2C%20that%20the%202020%20election%20results%20were%20wrong%20and%20that%20Trump%2C%20not%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20was%20the%20real%20winner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20statewide%20audit%20of%20the%20election%20results%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20concluded%20that%20Biden%20did%20indeed%20win%20the%20state's%20electoral%20college%20votes.%20And%20an