20coming%20to%20kill%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Freeman%20told%20jurors.%20%26quot%3BThey%20had%20my%20address.%20They%20had%20my%20phone%20number%2C%20my%20name.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGiuliani%20presented%20no%20defense%20in%20the%20trial%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20testimony%20echoed%20what%20Freeman%20and%20Moss%2C%20who%20are%20Black%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblack-georgia-election-worker-shaye-moss-glad-2020-not-1920-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20to%20Congressional%20investigators%3C%2Fa%3E%20examining%20the%20pro-Trump%20riot%20at%20the%20Capitol%20on%20January%206%2C%202021%2C%20where%20protesters%20tried%20to%20stop%20Congress%20from%20certifying%20the%20election%20results.%20Moss%20said%20she%20received%20a%20Facebook%20message%20telling%20her%20to%20%26quot%3Bbe%20glad%20it's%202020%20and%20not%201920%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20apparent%20reference%20to%20lynchings.%20And%20the%20supposed%20%26quot%3BUSB%20ports%26quot%3B%20Giuliani%20raged%20about%3F%20Moss%20said%20her%20mother%20had%20given%20her%20%26quot%3Ba%20ginger%20mint.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20start%2C%20Giuliani%20struggled%20to%20muster%20a%20defense%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeorgia-election-workers-sue-rudy-giuliani-oan-election-fraud-claims-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20lawsuit%2C%20which%20was%20first%20filed%20in%20December%20of%202021%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20didn't%20always%20mention%20Moss%20and%20Freeman%20by%20name%2C%20and%20that%20the%20Trump%20Campaign%2C%20not%20him%2C%20came%20up%20with%20the%20plan%20to%20blame%20them%20for%20the%20election%20results.%20US%20District%20Judge%20Beryl%20Howell%2C%20who's%20overseeing%20the%20case%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.dcd.238720%2Fgov.uscourts.dcd.238720.31.0_1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enoted%20in%20a%20ruling%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20was%20clear%20Giuliani%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20election%20workers%20when%20he%20espoused%20his%20%26quot%3Bincreasingly%20outlandish%20paranoia%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.dcd.238720%2Fgov.uscourts.dcd.238720.26.3_1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20document%20offered%20to%20the%20Trump%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%20identified%20him%20as%20the%20key%20person%20to%20orchestrate%20and%20execute%20the%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiuliani%20subsequently%20dragged%20his%20feet%20and%20failed%20to%20produce%20volumes%20of%20discovery%20evidence%20in%20the%20case%2C%20missing%20deadline%20after%20deadline.%20In%20one%20line%20of%20argument%2C%20explaining%20his%20delays%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20depending%20on%20the%20FBI%20to%20keep%20his%20electronic%20files%20organized%2C%20but%20they%20had%20created%20a%20mess%20of%20them%20after%20seizing%20them%20for%20a%20criminal%20investigation%20earlier%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22rudy%20giuliani%20ted%20goodman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b210c7a3c8094d5dceea7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERudy%20Giuliani%2C%20the%20former%20personal%20lawyer%20for%20former%20U.S.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20speaks%20to%20the%20press%20as%20he%20leaves%20the%20E.%20Barrett%20Prettyman%20U.S.%20District%20Courthouse.%3Cp%3EDrew%20Angerer%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHowell%2C%20in%20a%20scathing%20and%20incredulous%20August%20decision%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frudy-giuliani-sanctioned-georgia-defamation-case-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehanded%20Giuliani%20an%20automatic%20loss%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20not%20the%20FBI's%20job%20to%20preserve%20his%20electronic%20devices%20for%20a%20lawsuit%20he%20had%20known%20was%20coming%2C%20she%20said.%20The%20judge%20ordered%20Giuliani%20and%20his%20company%20to%20pay%20%24132%2C000%20to%20lawyers%20for%20Freeman%20and%20Moss%20for%20wasting%20everyone's%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20fatal%20blow%20to%20Giuliani's%20defense.%20The%20jurors%20could%20assume%20by%20default%20that%20Giuliani's%20remarks%20about%20Freeman%20and%20Moss%20were%20false%20and%20defamatory%2C%20the%20judge%20said.%20The%20only%20thing%20to%20be%20decided%20in%20the%20trial%20was%20the%20damages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAshlee%20Humphries%2C%20a%20marketing%20professor%20at%20Northwestern%20University%2C%20created%20a%20mathematical%20model%20for%20Freeman%20and%20Moss%20to%20put%20a%20dollar%20number%20on%20the%20damages.%20At%20the%20trial%2C%20she%20testified%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frudy-giuliani-caused-47-million-damage-georgia-election-workers-expert-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit%20would%20take%20up%20to%20%2447.5%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20run%20a%20restorative%20reputational%20campaign%20to%20effectively%20reverse%20the%20damage%20stemming%20from%20Giuliani's%20statements%20at%20issue%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiuliani's%20only%20move%20was%20to%20disperse%20blame.%20Joseph%20D.%20Sibley%2C%20his%20attorney%2C%20told%20jurors%20that%20Giuliani%20was%20just%20one%20part%20of%20a%20big%20election-denying%20machine%20working%20for%20Trump.%20Giuliani%20didn't%20personally%20make%20the%20threats%20against%20Freeman%20and%20Moss%20and%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20people%26quot%3B%20were%20to%20blame%2C%20he%20said.%20Freeman%20and%20Moss%20also%20have%20another%20lawsuit%20pending%20against%20the%20far-right%20media%20outlet%20The%20Gateway%20Pundit%20and%20its%20publisher%20Jim%20Hoft%2C%20who%20has%20pushed%20some%20of%20the%20same%20conspiracy%20theories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20all%20on%20the%20same%20hate%20train%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Moss%20testified%20on%20the%20wit