documents%20for%20his%20side%20of%20the%20case%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frudy-giuliani-wont-testify-defamation-trial-georgia-poll-workers-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGiuliani%20backed%20down%20and%20declined%20to%20testify%20in%20his%20defense%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESibley%20presented%20no%20other%20expert%20testimony%20to%20contradict%20Humphries's%20estimates.%20In%20cross-examining%20her%2C%20he%20raised%20whether%20other%20factors%20would%20mitigate%20the%20damage%20she%20calculated%2C%20like%20the%20fact%20that%20Georgia%20election%20officials%20cleared%20Freeman%20and%20Moss%20of%20wrongdoing.%20He%20also%20questioned%20whether%20the%20whole%20exercise%20of%20%26quot%3Breputational%20repair%26quot%3B%20was%20pointless%2C%20given%20that%20some%20people%20will%20always%20believe%20in%20conspiracy%20theories%2C%20like%20people%20who%20believe%20the%20Earth%20is%20flat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowell%2C%20in%20tossing%20a%20last-ditch%20effort%20from%20Sibley%20to%20dismiss%20the%20case%2C%20rejected%20that%20reasoning%20Thursday.%20Election%20conspiracy%20theorists%20were%20not%20the%20same%20as%20%26quot%3Bflat%20Earthers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20and%20Georgia%20election%20officials%20never%20executed%20a%20marketing%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20no%20hifalutin%20campaign%20strategy%20like%20the%20one%20Mr.%20Giuliani%20prepared%20for%20the%20former%20president%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Gottlieb%2C%20a%20lawyer%20for%20Freeman%20and%20Moss%2C%20played%20a%20video%20of%20Giuliani's%20press%20conference%20remarks.%20It%20was%20evidence%2C%20he%20said%2C%20that%20Giuliani%20felt%20no%20sympathy%20for%20the%20harm%20Freeman%20and%20Moss%20suffered%20and%20had%20little%20concern%20for%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRuby%20Freeman%20and%20Shaye%20Moss%20are%20more%20than%20just%20two%20women%20in%20a%20grainy%20video%20in%20a%20State%20Farm%20Arena%2