r%20emails%2C%20watch%20YouTube%2C%20and%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20high-end%3Cp%3ETo%20some%20people%2C%20%26quot%3Bhigh-end%20Chromebook%26quot%3B%20might%20sound%20like%20an%20oxymoron.%20After%20all%2C%20Chrome%20machines%20aren't%20known%20for%20their%20power.%20But%20with%20a%20relatively%20high-end%20CPU%20and%20premium%202-in-1%20screen%2C%20the%20Acer%20Chromebook%20Spin%20714%20isn't%20just%20a%20great%20Chromebook%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20great%20laptop%2C%20straight%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Spin%20714's%20Intel%20Core%20i5-1335U%20is%2C%20as%20far%20as%20I%20can%20find%2C%20the%20best%20processor%20in%20any%20Chromebook.%20This%20means%20fast%20boot-up%20times%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20run%20loads%20of%20apps%20at%20once%20without%20lag.%20And%20unlike%20many%20cheaper%20models%2C%20the%20Spin%20714%20includes%20an%20Intel%20Iris%20Xe%20graphics%20card.%20That's%20certainly%20not%20the%20strongest%20on%20the%20market%2C%20but%20it's%20about%20the%20best%20you'll%20get%20in%20any%20Chromebook%2C%20and%20enough%20to%20play%20loads%20of%20games%20with%20simpler%20graphics%20and%20older%20titles%20(think%20pre-2015).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20the%20Spin%20714%20holds%20up%2C%20too.%20The%20touchscreen%20offers%20a%20Full%20HD%20resolution%20(1920%20x%201200)%20and%20is%20outfitted%20with%20a%20360%C2%B0%20hinge%2C%20making%20it%20perfect%20for%20dual%20use%20as%20a%20tablet.%20The%20HD%20webcam%20is%20a%20great%20perk%2C%20too.%20And%20at%20256GB%2C%20the%20Spin%20714%20offers%20more%20onboard%20storage%20than%20nearly%20any%20other%20Chromebook%2C%20which%20is%20useful%20if%20you%20want%20to%20work%20offline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Spin%20714's%20worst%20quality%20is%20its%20small%20screen%2C%20which%20is%20only%2014%20inches.%20But%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20this%20smaller%20size%20helps%20keep%20the%20laptop%20portable%20and%20easy%20to%20handle%2C%20even%20when%20it's%20in%20its%20tablet%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20that%2C%20the%20worst%20drawback%20is%20the%20cost%3A%20At%20a%20retail%20price%20of%20%24700%2C%20the%20Spin%20714%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20Chromebook%20models.%20But%20for%20the%20specs%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20worth%20the%20investment.%20And%20luckily%2C%20it's%20not%20hard%20to%20find%20it%20on%20sale%20for%20a%20better%20price%20%E2%80%94%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20Best%20Buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%202-in-1%20on%20a%20budget%3Cp%3EAnother%20member%20of%20the%20debut%20Chromebook%20Plus%20lineup%2C%20the%20Lenovo%20IdeaPad%20Flex%205i%20is%20a%202-in-1%20laptop%20that%20offers%20powerful%20performance%20on%20a%20budget.%20In%20terms%20of%20specs%2C%20it's%20actually%20stronger%20than%20our%20top%20pick%2C%20the%20Acer%20Chromebook%20Plus%20515%20%E2%80%94%20but%20some%20slight%20flaws%20keep%20it%20from%20taking%20the%20top%20slot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20let's%20look%20at%20the%20processor%3A%20The%20Flex%205i%20is%20outfitted%20with%20an%20Intel%20i3-1315U.%20That's%20the%20same%20general%20model%20as%20the%20CPU%20in%20the%20Plus%20515%2C%20but%20a%20generation%20newer%2C%20which%20means%20better%20performance%20and%20power%20efficiency.%20It's%20complemented%20by%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20RAM%20and%20storage%20%E2%80%94%208GB%20and%20128GB%2C%20respectively%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20same%20fantastic%20battery%20life.%20It%20also%20includes%20a%20microSD%20card%20reader%20you%20can%20use%20to%20manually%20expand%20your%20storage%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20on%20top%20of%20those%20top-tier%20specs%2C%20you've%20got%20the%20benefit%20of%20a%20Full%20HD%2014-inch%20touchscreen%20with%20a%20360%C2%B0%20hinge%2C%20making%20it%20a%20fantastic%20tablet%20option.%20At%20a%20normal%20retail%20price%20of%20%24500%20(with%20common%20discounts%20bringing%20it%20even%20lower)%2C%20the%20Flex%205i%20is%20easily%20the%20best%202-in-1%20Chromebook%20you%20can%20get%20on%20a%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you're%20just%20looking%20for%20a%20good%20Chromebook%20and%20don't%20care%20about%20the%20touchscreen%2C%20I'd%20stick%20with%20the%20Plus%20515.%20Aside%20from%20the%20higher%20price%2C%20the%20Flex%205i%20has%20a%20smaller%20screen%2C%20and%20it%20lacks%20an%20HDMI%20or%20DisplayPort%20slot%2C%20so%20you%20can't%20connect%20it%20to%20an%20external%20display%20unless%20your%20monitor%20has%20a%20USB-C%20video%20port%20or%20you%20buy%20an%20adapter.%20It's%20also%20a%20half-pound%20heavier%20than%20the%20Spin%20714%2C%20which%20is%20a%20good%20upgrade%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20gaming%20and%20content%20creation%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20gaming%2C%20Chromebooks%20aren't%20exactly%20powerhouses.%20But%20in%20the%20world%20of%20cloud%20gaming%2C%20where%20all%20that%20really%20matters%20is%20your%20internet%20speed%20and%20screen%20quality%2C%20the%20Acer%20Chromebook%20516%20GE%20is%20a%20clear%20standout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20an%20Intel%20Core%20i5-1240P%20processor%2C%20Intel%20Iris%20Xe%20graphics%2C%208GB%20of%20RAM%2C%20and%20256GB%20of%20storage%2C%20the%20516%20GE%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20Chromebooks%20out%20there.%20This%20means%20fast%20load%20times%2C%20lots%20of%20multitasking%2C%20and%20great%20performance%20from%20content%20creation%20apps%20like%20Adobe%20Lightroom%20and%20BandLab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20516%20GE's%20most%20striking%20feature%20isn't%20its%20internal%20hardware%2C%20but%20its%20screen.%20The%20516%20GE%20boasts%20a%20beautiful%20QHD%20(2560x1600)%2016-inch%20screen%20with%20a%20refresh%20rate%20of%20120Hz.%20That's%20double%20the%20refresh%20rate%20you'll%20find%20on%20most%20other%20Chromebooks%2C%20and%20a%20higher%20resolution%20than%20nearly%20any%20other%20too.%20Combine%20that%20with%20an%20RGB-backlit%20keyboard%2C%20and%20you%20have%20a%20laptop%20that%20looks%20as%20great%20as%20it%20performs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20high-end%20screen%20comes%20in%20handy%20for%20content%20creation%2C%20but%20also%20when%20you%20turn%20from%20work%20to%20play.%20Like%20all%20Chromebooks%2C%20the%20516%20GE%20is%20eligible%20for%20not%20only%20a%20free%20copy%20of%20Minecraft%2C%20but%20three%20free%20months%20of%20Nvidia's%20GeForce%20Now%20streaming%20service.%20This%20gives%20you%20access%20to%20fantastic%20games%20like%20Fortnite%2C%20Cyberpunk%202077%2C%20Forza%20Motorsport%2C%20and%20more%2C%20at%20high%20frame%20rates%20and%20resolutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20516%20GE's%20built-in%20Iris%20Xe%20graphics%20card%20also%20unlocks%20loads%20of%20great%20games%20that%20you%20can%20play%20natively%20from%20Steam%2C%20and%20nearly%20all%20mobile%20Android%20titles.%20It's%20a%20juggernaut%20of%20a%20Chromebook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20516%20GE's%20biggest%20drawbacks%20are%20the%20flaws%20you'd%20expect%20from%20any%20gaming%20laptop%3A%20It%20has%20loud%20fans%20and%20shorter%20battery%20life%20than%20other%20models.%20But%20with%20ChromeOS'%20current%20capabilities%2C%20you'll%20rarely%20ever%20push%20the%20516%20GE%20hard%20enough%20that%20these%20become%20real%20problems.%20At%20%24650%20it's%20also%20more%20expensive%20than%20other%20Chromebooks%2C%20though%20it%20often%20goes%20on%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20only%20gaming%20Chromebook%20on%20the%20market.%20I'm%20also%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipg_040517_best-chromebooks-20%26h%3D59c532da51b3ca207a626e85fdc5c7f951cf5977ece466c618e6120562ac0e8f%26postID%3D61b8efc6f2a36b1ac9f41323%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fbest-chromebook%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FASUS-Chromebook-i5-1135G7-Processor-CX5501FEA-AS562T%252Fdp%252FB0BSP4ZMGB%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAsus%20Chromebook%20Vibe%20CX55%20Flip%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20an%20older%20CPU%20and%20a%20higher%20price%2C%20but%20comes%20with%20more%20RAM%2C%20expandable%20storage%20space%2C%20and%20a%2014