al%20use%2C%20which%20is%20longer%20than%20pretty%20much%20any%20other%20Chromebook.%20The%20Duet%205%20also%20comes%20with%208GB%20of%20RAM%20and%20128GB%20of%20storage%2C%20which%20is%20similar%20to%20our%20top%20Chromebook%20Plus%20model%2C%20as%20well%20as%20an%20HD%20webcam%20and%20a%20wonderfully%20bright%20(400%20nits%20peak)%20OLED%20screen.%20All%20of%20this%20just%20adds%20to%20the%20Duet%205's%20portable%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20Duet%205's%20build%20also%20means%20that%20it%20doesn't%20have%20much%20room%20for%20ports.%20There%20are%20two%20USB-C%20ports%2C%20one%20of%20which%20is%20used%20for%20charging%E2%80%A6%20and%20that's%20it.%20It%20doesn't%20even%20have%20a%20headphone%20jack.%20You'll%20need%20a%20USB-C%20hub%20and%20Bluetooth%20headphones%20for%20this%20tablet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Duet%205's%20biggest%20flaw%20is%20its%20price.%20It%20currently%20retails%20exclusively%20from%20Best%20Buy%20at%20%24500%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20incredibly%20overpriced%20compared%20to%20stronger%20Chromebooks.%20You're%20paying%20for%20portability%20here%2C%20not%20power%2C%20which%20won't%20be%20worth%20it%20to%20all%20consumers.%20But%20the%20Duet%205%20offers%20a%20blend%20of%20size%20and%20performance%20that%20you%20won't%20find%20in%20other%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20test%20Chromebooks%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222696%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Acer%20Chromebook%20Plus%20515%20sitting%20on%20a%20wooden%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652089e79f7ca8b2bbdcafce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222022%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Plus%20515's%20speakers%20are%20big%20and%20forward-facing.%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Antonelli%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20guide%20to%20the%20best%20Chromebook%20was%20put%20together%20using%20a%20combination%20of%20research%2C%20analysis%20of%20industry%20trends%2C%20comparison%20between%20models%2C%20and%20hands-on%20testing.%20This%20included%20benchmark%20testing%20between%20CPUs%2C%20and%20time%20spent%20using%20AI%20and%20cloud%20gaming%20apps%20made%20for%20Chromebook.%20I%20also%20cross-reference%20my%20opinions%20with%20other%20experts%20to%20see%20if%20my%20experiences%20were%20typical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20reviewing%2C%20I%20judge%20the%20best%20Chromebooks%20on%20a%20variety%20of%20qualities.%20How%20fast%20are%20they%3F%20What%20do%20they%20look%20like%3F%20How%20much%20do%20they%20weigh%3F%20And%20%E2%80%94%20most%20importantly%20for%20many%20users%20%E2%80%94%20how%20much%20do%20they%20cost%20compared%20to%20competing%20models%3F%20Even%20some%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20Chromebooks%20on%20the%20market%20simply%20aren't%20worth%20the%20price%2C%20especially%20for%20students%20or%20casual%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20debut%20of%20Chromebook%20Plus%20laptops%20has%20unlocked%20new%20possibilities%20for%20ChromeOS.%20I'm%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20keep%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20the%20industry%2C%20and%20I'll%20reevaluate%20this%20guide%20at%20multiple%20points%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%20replacing%20picks%20as%20needed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EChromebook%20FAQs%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222171%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Chromebook%20logo%20on%20the%20corner%20of%20a%20device.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5dc1dac07eece512d06a2754%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20Collection%2FGado%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20a%20Chromebook%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20computers%20in%20the%20world%20either%20run%20on%20Windows%20or%20macOS.%20But%20Chromebook%20laptops%20run%20on%20a%20unique%20operating%20system%20called%20ChromeOS%2C%20which%20is%20mostly%20based%20around%20running%20programs%20made%20by%20Google.%20This%20includes%20productivity%20cloud%20apps%20like%20Google%20Docs%20and%20Google%20Drive%2C%20but%20also%20sites%20that%20you%20use%20every%20day%2C%20like%20Gmail%20and%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20they%20rely%20so%20heavily%20on%20Google%20apps%2C%20Chromebooks%20can't%20run%20nearly%20as%20many%20programs%20as%20Windows%20or%20Mac%20devices.%20It's%20also%20harder%20to%20use%20them%20offline%2C%20since%20so%20many%20Google%20services%20need%20an%20internet%20connection.%20Chromebooks%20do%20let%20you%20download%20and%20use%20nearly%20any%20Android%20smartphone%20app%2C%20but%20compared%20to%20Windows%20and%20macOS%2C%20Chromebooks%20still%20don't%20have%20nearly%20as%20many%20available%20programs%20or%20customization%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20exchange%2C%20Chromebooks%20are%20routinely%20faster%20and%20more%20stable.%20They%20also%20offer%20far%20superior%20battery%20life%20and%20protection%20from%20malware%2C%20nearly%20all%20at%20affordable%20prices.%20There's%20a%20reason%20that%20Chromebooks%20have%20become%20so%20common%20in%20US%20classrooms%3A%20They're%20cheap%2C%20simple%20to%20use%2C%20and%20hard%20to%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20younger%20students%2C%20Chromebooks%20are%20mainly%20made%20for%20casual%20computer%20users.%20If%20all%20you%20need%20a%20laptop%20for%20is%20browsing%20the%20internet%2C%20watching%20videos%2C%20and%20using%20social%20media%2C%20Chromebooks%20are%20a%20great%20option.%20They'll%20also%20support%20light%20productivity%20work%2C%20like%20document%20and%20spreadsheet%20editing%2C%20or%20basic%20graphic%20design%20through%20web%20apps%20like%20Photoshop%20Online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat's%20the%20difference%20between%20Chromebook%20Plus%20laptops%20and%20other%20Chromebooks%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EChromebooks%20have%20been%20around%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20now.%20But%20in%20October%202023%2C%20Google%20announced%20the%20Chromebook%20Plus%20line%2C%20a%20series%20of%20laptops%20with%20top-tier%20specs%2C%20onboard%20AI%20tools%2C%20and%20loads%20of%20free%20pe