2C%20York%20College%2C%20and%20rent%20their%20indoor%2C%20six-lane%2C%2014-foot-deep%20pool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20our%20program%20expanding%20into%20a%20larger%20facility%20and%20larger%20city%20%E2%80%94%20and%20classes%20constantly%20selling%20out%20in%20the%20years%20prior%20%E2%80%94%20we%20needed%20more%20staff%20to%20support%20the%20demand.%20But%20as%20a%20smaller%2C%20niche%20brand%2C%20we%20weren't%20exempt%20from%20the%20uphill%20battle%20of%20sourcing%20staff%20in%20the%20aquatics%20industry%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flifeguard-labor-shortage-pools-cutting-opening-hours-closing-work-jobs-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epools%20across%20the%20city%20shut%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20lifeguard%20and%20staff%20shortages.%20Left%20without%20many%20options%2C%20I%20defaulted%20to%20what%20I%20knew%20would%20help%20me%20in%20this%20bind%3A%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCrZdCcegyAV%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo-minute%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20posted%20across%20all%20my%20social-media%20accounts%2C%20I%20issued%20a%20cry%20for%20help.%20My%20main%20statement%20was%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20cannot%20find%20more%20lifeguards%20and%20swim%20instructors%20this%20summer%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20Black%20People%20Will%20Swim.%20And%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20there%20will%20be%20more%20drownings%20in%20our%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20we%20secured%2013%20water-safety%20instructors%20and%20lifeguards%2C%20eight%20volunteers%2C%20five%20student%20workers%2C%20and%20a%20short-lived%20aquatics%20director.%20Going%20up%20against%20the%20NYC%20Department%20of%20Parks%20%26amp%3B%20Recreation%20and%20local%20swim%20businesses%20was%20challenging%2C%20but%20we%20held%20our%20own%20and%20taught%20over%20400%20students%20this%20summer%20thanks%20to%20our%20fantastic%20team.%20Despite%20our%20success%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexperts-advice-on-attracting-and-retaining-workers-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehiring%20and%20retaining%20a%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20frustrating%20%E2%80%94%20I%20might%20even%20go%20as%20far%20as%20to%20say%20it%20was%20strenuous%20%E2%80%94%20but%20these%20four%20actions%20helped%20me%20beat%20the%20odds%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Being%20a%20mission-driven%20brand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20starters%2C%20BPWS%20is%20a%20mission-driven%20brand%20created%20to%20make%20swimming%20equitable%2C%20affordable%2C%20and%20accessible%20for%20Black%20people.%20Why%3F%20According%20to%20the%20CDC%2C%20Black%20children%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2010%20and%2014%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fdrowning%2Ffacts%2Findex.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520swimming%2520pools%252C%2520Black%2520children%2Cto%2520drown%2520in%2520residential%2520pools.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrown%207.6%20times%20more%20frequently%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20Caucasian%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Fuse%20Marketing's%20survey%2C%2085%25%20of%20surveyed%20Gen%20Zers%20and%2070%25%20of%20surveyed%20Millennials%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20engage%20with%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-small-businesses-include-social-causes-in-their-marketing-strategy-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20a%20brand%20that%20supports%20a%20social%20cause%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20one%20that%20doesn't.%20With%20our%20tagline%20being%20%26quot%3Bempowering%20and%20educating%20Black%20people%20to%20conquer%20their%20fears%20and%20learn%20how%20to%20swim%2C%26quot%3B%20many%20people%2C%20regardless%20of%20race%2C%20are%20drawn%20to%20the%20mission%20and%20vision%20of%20the%20brand%20and%20help%20make%20a%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Zers%2C%20millennials%2C%20and%20even%20boomers%20want%20to%20work%20for%20a%20brand%20they%20know%20is%20making%20a%20difference%20in%20the%20community.%20And%20while%20our%20starting%20pay%20is%20%2418%20an%20hour%2C%20we%20offer%20lower-cost%20swim%20lessons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Providing%20free%20certifications%20and%20other%20incentives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20running%20a%20swim%20program%2C%20one%20must%20fulfill%20several%20requirements%20to%20prevent%20the%20Department%20of%20Health%20from%20shutting%20it%20down%2C%20such%20as%20having%20certified%20lifeguards%20and%20water-safety%20instructors%20on%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20can%20gain%20certifications%2C%20which%20can%20cost%20between%20%24350%20to%20%24500%2C%20via%20the%20American%20Red%20Cross%2C%20the%20YMCA%2C%20or%20the%20city's%20parks%20department.%20But%20due%20to%20the%20uncertain%20future%20the%20pandemic%20left%20the%20aquatics%20industry%20in%2C%20many%20people%20had%20certifications%20that%20have%20expired%20or%20lapsed.%20To%20supplement%20that%2C%20we%20hired%20individuals%20and%20covered%20the%20cost%20of%20their%20certifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20we%20sent%20a%20team%20of%20five%20to%20gain%20their%20water-safety-instructor%20certification%20by%20the%20American%20Red%20Cross.%20This%20amounted%20to%20%242%2C400%2C%20which%20is%20quite%20an%20expense%20for%20a%20small%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20our%20volunteers%2C%20we%20were%20intentional%20with%20the%20name%20by%20calling%20them%20our%20%26quot%3BDo-Gooders.%26quot%3B%20Being%20a%20Do-Gooder%20was%20a%20reminder%20that%20working%20for%20BPWS%20is%20all%20about%20doing%20good%20and%20that%20no%20job%20is%20insignificant%20or%20worth%20more%20than%20another.%20We%20also%20offered%20them%20free%20swim%20lessons%20as%20an%20incentive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Fostering%20a%20fun%20yet%20professional%20environment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20small%20business%2C%20I%20understand%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-midsize-companies-highly-rated-company-culture-comparably-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimportance%20of%20fostering%20a%20fun%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20yet%20professional%20environment.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20I%20went%20the%20extra%20mile%20by%20hosting%20our%20yearly%20end-of-summer%20team%20dinner%20in%20Astoria%2C%20a%20neighborhood%20in%20Queens%2C%20as%20a%20token%20of%20appreciation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwimming%20is%20a%20physically%20demanding%20job%20where%20one%20must%20be%20in%20good%20health%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can't%20afford%20being%20sick%20while%20teaching%20in%20the%20water.%20Therefore%2C%20teaching%20400%20students%20in%20four%20months%20is%20no%20easy%20feat%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20let%20the%20team%20know%20that%20I%20appreciate%20their%20hard%20work.%20Every%20year%20since%20I%20started%20the%20business%2C%20I've%20always%20hosted%20end-of-the-season%20team%20dinners%2C%20which%20have%20become%20a%20staple%20BPWS%20tradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Asking%20your%20community%20for%20help%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20age%20of%20social%20media%2C%20where%20one's%20social-media%20feed%20is%20a%20highlight%20reel%2C%20I%20was%20never%20the%20type%20to%20fake%20the%20funk%20and%20pretend%20that%20running%20a%20business%20is%20great.%20With%20the%20spring%20session%20quickly%20approaching%20and%20members%20anticipating%20the%20next%20swim%20session%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20be%20honest%20about%20my%20situation%20%E2%80%94%20we%20were%20short-staffed%20and%20unsure%20about%20hosting%20a%20swim%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-promote-business-on-social-media-go-viral-influencers-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewent%20to%20social%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20shared%20my%20transgressions.%20That%20video%20was%20shared%20946%20times%2C%20played%20nearly%2047%2C400%20times%2C%20and%20received%20213%20comments.%20We%20received%20countless%20messages%20and%20applications%20from%