self%20and%20his%20family%2C%20and%20requested%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20intervene%20in%20his%20extradition%20to%20the%20US.%20The%20hearing%20has%20been%20adjourned%20till%20January%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20he%20was%20intercepted%20by%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20agents%26quot%3B%20on%20his%20arrival%20in%20Prague%2C%20then%20bundled%20into%20a%20black%20SUV%20and%20interrogated%20for%20three%20hours%20while%20being%20driven%20around%20the%20foreign%20city.%20He%20claimed%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bforced%26quot%3B%20to%20eat%20only%20pork%20and%20beef%20during%20his%20first%20few%20days%20in%20the%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20Gupta%20has%20been%20charged%20by%20US%20federal%20prosecutors%20with%20working%20with%20an%20Indian%20government%20employee%20in%20the%20foiled%20plot%20to%20kill%20Pannun%2C%20a%20designated%20terrorist%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20had%20alleged%20the%20role%20of%20Indian%20agents%20in%20the%20June%20murder%20of%20another%20Khalistani%20terrorist%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20Canadian%20citizen.%20India%20had%20rejected%20the%20allegations%20as%20%26quot%3Bmotivated%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702665000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-03%2Findia-us_650x400_41457064040.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-american-lawmakers-on-murder-plot-charge-if-not-addressed-4681477%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian-American%20Congress%20members%20have%20expressed%20deep%20concern%20over%20an%20Indian%20being%20charged%20with%20an%20alleged%20plot%20to%20kill%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20an%20American-Canadian%20citizen.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-american-lawmakers-on-murder-plot-charge-if-not-addressed-4681477%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22h