rty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Income%20Tax%20searches%20against%20a%20firm%2C%20Boudh%20Distillery%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20and%20associated%20entities%20owned%20by%20Mr%20Sahu's%20family%20began%20on%20December%206%20and%20ended%20on%20Friday.%20Carried%20out%20in%20Odisha%20and%20Jharkhand%2C%20the%20searches%20yielded%20cash%20worth%20Rs%20353.5%20crore%2C%20marking%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdhiraj-sahu-income-tax-raids-odisha-rs-353-crore-cash-haul-in-searches-against-congress-mp-officials-go-hi-tech-to-find-hidden-gold-4677443%5C%22%3Elargest%20single%20seizure%3C%2Fa%3E%20ever%20made%20by%20any%20investigative%20agency%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20record%20recovery%2C%20long%20search%20and%20videos%20of%20almirahs%20full%20of%20cash%20have%20been%20used%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20slam%20the%20Congress%20and%20accuse%20it%20of%20corruption.%20Even%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20party%20using%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20popular%20TV%20series%20'Money%20Heist'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20Mr%20Sahu%20said%20he%20has%20been%20in%20active%20politics%20for%20nearly%2035%20years%20and%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20such%20an%20allegation%20has%20been%20levelled%20at%20him.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20hurt%2C%20and%20I%20can%20say%20with%20conviction%20that%20the%20money%20that%20has%20been%20recovered%20is%20my%20firm's.%20We%20have%20been%20in%20the%20liquor%20business%20for%20over%20100%20years.%20I%20am%20involved%20in%20politics%20and%20did%20not%20pay%20much%20attention%20to%20the%20business.%20That%20was%20looked%20after%20by%20my%20family%2C%20and%20I%20would%20just%20ask%20how%20things%20were%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20Hindi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Jharkhand%20said%20his%20is%20a%20big%2C%20joint%20family%20and%20six%20brothers%2C%20including%20him%2C%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20business.%20Their%20children%20also%20look%20after%20various%20aspects%20of%20the%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20money%20that%20has%20been%20recovered%20is%20related%20to%20our%20firms%20involved%20in%20the%20liquor%20business.%20Our%20business%20is%20transparent.%20The%20money%20is%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20alcohol%20and%20it%20is%20in%20cash%20because%20sales%20in%20the%20liquor%20business%20happen%20in%20cash.%20The%20cash%20was%20from%20sales%20collections%20and%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20Congress%20or%20any%20other%20party.%20It%20is%20the%20money%20of%20my%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20firms%20belong%20to%20my%20relatives%20and%20no%20money%20has%20been%20recovered%20from%20the%20premises%20of%20Boudh%20Distillery%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20where%20some%20of%20the%20liquor%20is%20made.%20The%20money%20is%20not%20mine%2C%20it%20is%20my%20family's%20as%20well%20as%20of%20related%20companies.%20My%20family%20members%20will%20give%20clarifications%2C%20if%20needed%2C%20to%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department.%20We%20will%20cooperate%20with%20the%20authorities%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sahu%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702659540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fqncle7j_dhiraj-sahu-ani_625x300_15_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-my-money-but-congress-mp-dhirag-sahu-first-reaction-on-rs-350-crore-cash-haul-4681046%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Breaking%20his%20silence%20after%2010%20days%20on%20the%20record%20Rs%20350%20crore%20in%20cash%20seized%20from%20premises%20linked%20to%20him%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Dhiraj%20Sahu%20on%20Friday%20said%20that%20his%20family%20handles%20the%20business%20and%20the%20money%20recovered%20is%20not%20his.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-my-money-but-congress-mp-dhirag-sahu-first-reac