%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01141008%2FPannun-FP.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20a%20joint%20statement%2C%20Indian-American%20legislators%20in%20the%20US%20Congress%20have%20cautioned%20that%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20the%20United%20States%20could%20face%20%E2%80%9Csignificant%20damage%E2%80%9D%20if%20there%20is%20not%20enough%20accountability%20for%20allegations%20made%20of%20the%20involvement%20of%20an%20Indian%20government%20official%20in%20a%20plot%20to%20kill%20a%20US%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-assassination-plot-india-enquiry-committee-set-up%5C%22%3ELast%20month%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20US%20federal%20prosecutors%20released%20a%20new%20and%20detailed%20indictment%20of%20an%20Indian%20national%2C%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20for%20attempting%20to%20hire%20a%20hitman%20to%20kill%20a%20Sikh%20separatist.%20The%20indictment%20accused%20an%20unnamed%20but%20identified%20Indian%20government%20official%20(%E2%80%98CC-1%E2%80%99)%20of%20recruiting%20Gupta%20for%20orchestrating%20the%20conspiracy.%20Gupta%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%2C%20facing%20extradition%20proceedings%20initiated%20by%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkhanna.house.gov%2Fmedia%2Fpress-releases%2Frepresentatives-khanna-bera-jayapal-krishnamoorthi-and-thanedar-celebrate%5C%22%3EThe%20joint%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20released%20on%20Friday%20on%20behalf%20of%20five%20Indian%20American%20lawmakers%20currently%20serving%20in%20the%20118%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20Ami%20Bera%2C%20Pramila%20Jayapal%2C%20Ro%20Khanna%2C%20Raja%20Krishnamoorthi%20and%20Shri%20Thanedar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20noted%20that%20they%20had%20received%20a%20closed-door%20classified%20briefing%20from%20the%20US%20administration%20on%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20appreciate%20the%20Administration%20providing%20us%20a%20classified%20briefing%20on%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%E2%80%99s%20indictment%20of%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20which%20alleges%20that%20an%20Indian%20government%20official%20engaged%20in%20a%20murder-for-hire%20plot%20of%20an%20American%20citizen%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reference%20to%20%E2%80%9Cclassified%E2%80%9D%20presumably%20means%20that%20the%20legislators%20have%20been%20read%20in%20to%20more%20details%20about%20the%20plot%2C%20including%20its%20%3Cem%3Edramatis%20personae%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20evidence%20US%20investigators%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20the%20safety%20and%20well-being%20of%20their%20constituents%20were%20of%20utmost%20priority%2C%20the%20five%20lawmakers%20noted%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Callegations%20made%20in%20the%20indictment%20are%20deeply%20concerning%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWelcoming%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20of%20enquiry%2C%20the%20statement%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccritical%20that%20India%20fully%20investigate%2C%20hold%20those%20responsible%2C%20including%20Indian%20government%20officials%2C%20accountable%2C%20and%20provide%20assurances%20that%20this%20will%20not%20happen%20again%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20cautioned%20that%20if%20there%20was%20no%20proper%20accountability%2C%20this%20would%20impact%20the%20bilateral%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20the%20US%E2%80%93India%20partnership%20has%20made%20a%20meaningful%20impact%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20both%20of%20our%20people%2C%20but%20we%20are%20concerned%20that%20the%20actions%20outlined%20in%20the%20indictment%20could%2C%20if%20not%20appropriately%20addressed%2C%20cause%20significant%20damage%20to%20this%20very%20consequential%20partnership%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20allegations%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20public%20accusation%20made%20by%20Canada%20that%20there%20was%20a%20potential%20link%20of%20Indian%20agents%20to%20the%20June%2018%2C%202023%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20Canadian%20national%C2%A0%20and%20Sikh%20activist%20who%20was%20declared%20a%20terrorist%20by%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20indictment%20seemed%20to%20indicate%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20official%20(CC-1)%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar.%20The%20%E2%80%98victim%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20US%20court%20filings%20was%20not%20publicly%20identified%2C%20but%20he%20is%20understood%20to%20be%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20%E2%80%98General%20Counsel%E2%80%99%20for%20%E2%80%98Sikhs%20for%20Justice%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20banned%20as%20a%20terror%20group%20by%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%20had%20reacted%20angrily%20to%20the%20Canadian%20allegations%2C%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20US%20charges%20has%20been%20substantially%20different.%20India%20announced%20that%20it%20had%20set%20up%20a%20high-level%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinputs%E2%80%9D%20provided%20by%20US%2C%20which%20it%20continued%20to%20relate%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnexus%20between%20organized%20criminals%2C%20gun%20runners%2C%20terrorists%20and%20others%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702659344000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01141008%2FPannun-FP.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-murder-plot-significant-damage-likely-for-bilateral-ties-warn-indian-american-lawmakers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Five%20US%20Congress%20members%20said%20in%20a%20joint%20statement%20that%20it%20is%20critical%20for%20India%20to%20%26quot%3Bfully%20investigate%20%5Band%5D%20hold%20those%20responsible%2C%20including%20Indian%20government%20officials%2C%20accountable%2C%20and%20provide%20assurances%20that%20this%20wil