et-approves-proposal-for-international-status-to-surat-airport-4680938%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Humans%20Are%20Fueling%20Global%20Warming%20By%20Just%20Breathing%2C%20Study%20Claims%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EScientists%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20have%20published%20new%20research%20that%20claims%20that%20humans%20are%20exhaling%20global%20warming-causing%20gases%20when%20they%20breathe.%20The%20study%20has%20been%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20PLOS%20One.%20Experts%20explained%20that%20methane%20and%20nitrous%20oxide%20in%20the%20air%20we%20exhale%20make%20up%20to%200.1%25%20of%20the%20UK's%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions.%20So%20once%20you%20factor%20in%20the%20farts%20and%20burps%20being%20produced%20by%20humans%2C%20it%20becomes%20clear%20that%20humans%20are%20fueling%20global%20warming%20by%20just%20exhaling%20from%20lungs%2C%20scientists%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.plos.org%2Fplosone%2Farticle%3Fid%3D10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0295157%5C%22%3Enew%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20led%20by%20Dr%20Nicholas%20Cowan%20from%20the%20UK%20Centre%20for%20Ecology%20and%20Hydrology%20in%20Edinburgh.%20In%20the%20paper%2C%20she%20said%20that%20the%20evidence%20of%20planet-killing%20breathing%20is%20pretty%20clear%20and%20it%20shouldn't%20be%20ignored.%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20urge%20caution%20in%20the%20assumption%20that%20emissions%20from%20humans%20are%20negligible%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20of%20researchers%20explained%20that%20when%20humans%20inhale%2C%20air%20enters%20the%20lungs%20and%20oxygen%20from%20that%20air%20moves%20to%20the%20blood%2C%20while%20carbon%20dioxide%20(CO2)%2C%20a%20waste%20gas%2C%20moves%20from%20the%20blood%20to%20the%20lungs%20and%20is%20breathed%20out.%20Every%20person%20breathes%20out%20CO2%20when%20they%20exhale%2C%20but%20in%20the%20new%20study%2C%20researchers%20focused%20on%20methane%20and%20nitrous%20oxide.%20They%20explained%20that%20these%20two%20are%20both%20powerful%20greenhouse%20gases%2C%20but%20because%20they%20are%20breathed%20out%20in%20much%20smaller%20quantities%2C%20their%20contribution%20to%20global%20warming%20may%20have%20been%20overlooked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20report%20only%20emissions%20in%20breath%20in%20this%20study%2C%20and%20flatus%20emissions%20are%20likely%20to%20increase%20these%20values%20significantly%2C%20though%20no%20literature%20characterises%20these%20emissions%20for%20people%20in%20the%20UK%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20team%20wrote%20in%20the%20study.%20%26quot%3BAssuming%20that%20livestock%20and%20other%20wild%20animals%20also%20exhale%20emissions%20of%20N2O%2C%20there%20may%20still%20be%20a%20small%20but%20significant%20unaccounted-for%20source%20of%20N2O%20emissions%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20which%20could%20account%20for%20more%20than%201%25%20of%20national-scale%20emissions%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fscientist-develop-first-mind-reading-helmet-that-can-write-what-you-think-4675048%5C%22%3EScientist%20Develop%20First%20Mind-Reading%20Helmet%20That%20Can%20Write%20What%20You%20Think%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20study%2C%20the%20researchers%20investigated%20emissions%20of%20methane%20and%20nitrous%20oxide%20in%20human%20breath%20from%20104%20adult%20volunteers%20in%20the%20UK.%20After%20analysing%20they%20found%20that%20nitrous%20oxide%20was%20emitted%20by%20every%20participant%2C%20but%20methane%20was%20found%20in%20the%20breath%20of%20only%2031%20per%20cent%20of%20participants.%20The%20team%20said%20that%20those%20who%20do%20not%20exhale%20methane%20in%20their%20breath%20are%20still%20likely%20to%20%26quot%3Brelease%20gas%20ion%20flatus%26quot%3B%2C%20meaning%20by%20farting%20or%20burping.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20concentrations%20of%20the%20two%20gases%20in%20the%20overall%20samples%20let%20the%20researchers%20estimate%20the%20proportion%20of%20the%20UK's%20emissions%20from%20human%20breath%20-%200.05%20per%20cent%20for%20methane%20and%200.1%20per%20cent%20for%20nitrous%20oxide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearchers%20didn't%20manage%20to%20find%20any%20link%20between%20gases%20in%20the%20breath%20and%20diets.%20%26quot%3BConcentration%20enhancement%20of%20both%20CH4%20and%20N2O%20in%20the%20breath%20of%20vegetarians%20and%20meat%20consumers%20are%20similar%20in%20magnitude.%20Based%20on%20these%20results%2C%20we%20can%20state%20that%2C%20when%20estimating%20emissions%20from%20a%20population%20within%20the%20UK%2C%20diet%20or%20future%20diet%20changes%20are%20unlikely%20to%20be%20important%20when%20estimating%20emissions%20across%20the%20UK%20as%20a%20whole%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20study%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702657020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fakf0c8vo_breathing-generic_625x300_15_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fhumans-are-fueling-global-warming-by-just-breathing-study-claims-4680910%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Scientists%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20have%20published%20new%20research%20that%20claims%20that%20humans%20are%20exhaling%20global%20warming-causing%20gases%20when%20they%20breathe.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fhumans-are-fueling-global-warming-by-just-breathing-study-claims-4680910%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fhumans-are-fueling-global-warming-by-just-breathing-study-claims-4680910%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fhumans-are-fueling-global-warming-by-just-breathing-study-claims-4680910%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SRK%2C%20Suhana%2C%20Gauri%20attend%20AbRam's%20school%20event%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702656994000%