y%20by%20the%20Centre%2C%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmuting%E2%80%9D%20the%20mention%20of%20Palestine%20in%20their%20sermons%20on%20Fridays%20at%20the%20mosques%20across%20the%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20%E2%80%9Cverbal%20instructions%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20authorities%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Wakf%20Board%2C%20which%20runs%20shrines%20across%20the%20Union%20territory%2C%20some%20preachers%20alleged%20that%20they%20were%20asked%20to%20%E2%80%9Cavoid%20mentioning%20the%20Palestine%20issue%E2%80%9D%20during%20the%20annual%20festival%20of%20a%20prominent%20Sufi%20saint%20at%20a%20shrine%20in%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecurity%20personnel%20were%20also%20monitoring%20the%20sermons%20being%20made%20and%20had%20also%20conveyed%20against%20arousing%20passions%20over%20the%20subject%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20two%20anonymous%20preachers%20as%20saying%20on%20November%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20sporadic%20protests%20broke%20out%20in%20Kashmir%20parts%20over%20a%20%E2%80%98blasphemous%E2%80%99%20social%20media%20post%20by%20a%20student%20at%20the%20prestigious%20National%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20in%20Srinagar%20with%20a%20top%20police%20official%20claiming%20that%20a%20conspiracy%20was%20being%20hatched%20%E2%80%9Cacross%20the%20border%E2%80%9D%20to%20use%20anger%20against%20the%20post%20for%20%E2%80%9Cother%20things%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702655439000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13155820%2FIMG_0834.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsrinagar-prayers-at-jamia-masjid-barred-for-10th-consecutive-friday-mirwaiz-put-under-house-arrest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anjuman%20Auqaf%20Jama%20Masjid%2C%20the%20managing%20body%20of%20the%2014th-century%20mosque%2C%20said%20no%20reason%20was%20cited%20for%20the%20restrictions%20on%20prayers%20at%20the%20historic%20mosque.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A