%20linked%20to%20a%20banned%20outfit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Investigating%20Agency%20conducted%20the%20raids%20in%2023%20locations%20across%20Jharkhand%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20New%20Delhi.%20The%20case%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20People's%20Liberation%20Front%20of%20India%2C%20a%20banned%20outfit%20based%20in%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArms%2C%20ammunition%2C%20incriminating%20documents%20and%20devices%2C%20cash%20and%20jewellery%20were%20also%20found%20during%20the%20raids%2C%20the%20NIA%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20suspects%20who%20faced%20the%20crackdown%20were%20%26quot%3Bcadres%20and%20sympathizers%20of%20PLFI%26quot%3B%2C%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20carry%20out%20violent%20acts%20and%20commit%20terrorist%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%2023%20locations%20searched%20today%2C%2019%20were%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20two%20in%20Delhi%2C%20and%20one%20each%20in%20Bihar%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20The%20two%20arrested%20during%20the%20raids%20were%20identified%20as%20Raman%20Kumar%20Sonu%20from%20Bihar%20and%20Nivesh%20Kumar%20from%20Delhi%2C%20both%20named%20as%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20said%20the%20central%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20searches%2C%20two%20Pistols%2C%20live%20rounds%20(7.86%20mm)%2C%20Rs%203%2C00%2C000%20in%20cash%2C%20incriminating%20materials%2C%20including%20digital%20devices%20(mobile%20phones%2C%20SIM%20cards%2C%20pen%20drives%2C%20DVR)%20and%20documents%20(diary%20and%20a%20bunch%20of%20papers)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20gold%20and%20silver%20jewellery%20were%20seized%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20Indian%20Army%20uniform%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%20said%20its%20probe%20has%20revealed%20that%20the%20PLFI%20cadres%20have%20been%20extorting%20money%20from%20coal%20traders%2C%20railway%20contractors%20and%20businessmen%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Odisha%20to%20finance%20their%20terror%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20also%20conspiring%20to%20commit%20various%20terrorist%20activities%2C%20including%20attacks%20on%20the%20security%20forces%2C%20murder%2C%20arson%2C%20and%20use%20of%20explosives%2FIEDs%20to%20create%20terror%20in%20the%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NIA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20PLFI%20was%20also%20involved%20in%20recruitment%20and%20procurement%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunition%2C%20besides%20conspiring%20to%20revive%20and%20expand%20their%20outfit%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702651440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-12%2F9cmll0r_nia-generic-650_625x300_27_December_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-uniform-seized-during-raids-across-4-states-in-terror-financing-case-4680572%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20suspects%20were%20arrested%20and%20an%20army%20uniform%20was%20seized%20during%20raids%20on%20Friday%20by%20the%20central%20anti-terror%20agency%20across%20four%20states%20in%20a%20terror%20financing%20case%20linked%20to%20a%20banned%20outfit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-uniform-seized-during-raids-across-4-states-in-terror-financing-case-4680572%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-uniform-seized-during-raids-across-4-states-in-terror-financing-case-4680572%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-uniform-seized-during-raids-across-4-states-in-terror-financing-case-4680572%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aishwarya%20NOT%20living%20separately%20from%20Bachchan%20family%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702651375000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-10602986