%20health%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20case%2C%20lodged%20in%20the%20backward%20Sonbhadra%20district%2C%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20an%20office-bearer%20of%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%2C%20police%20booked%2042%20persons%20under%20Sections%203%20and%205%20(1)%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Prohibition%20of%20Unlawful%20Conversion%20of%20Religion%20Act%2C%202021.%20Nine%20persons%2C%20including%20a%20person%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20one%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20were%20arrested.%20In%20another%20case%2C%20police%20in%20Sant%20Kabir%20Nagar%20on%20December%2011%20arrested%20a%20couple%20originally%20from%20Kerala%20on%20charges%20of%20allegedly%20alluring%20a%20woman%20from%20the%20backward%20caste%20Nishad%20community%20to%20convert%20and%20for%20insulting%20Hindu%20deities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20creating%20a%20situation%20of%20caste%20conflict%2C%E2%80%9D%20Narsingh%20Tripathi%2C%20the%20VHP%20activist%20who%20lodged%20the%20police%20complaint%20in%20Sonbhadra%2C%20told%20The%20Wire%20on%20what%20motivated%20him%20to%20file%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2029%2C%20an%20FIR%20was%20registered%20at%20Chopan%20police%20station%20in%20Sonbhadra%20on%20Tripathi%E2%80%99s%20complaint%2C%20which%20alleged%20that%20the%20accused%20persons%20were%20trying%20to%20convert%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ebholi%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ebhali%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(na%C3%AFve)%20and%20deprived%20people%20living%20in%20the%20tribal%20dominated%20areas.%20They%20were%20also%20afflicted%20by%20superstition%2C%20Tripathi%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20named%2042%20persons%20including%20Christian%20social%20workers%20Jai%20Prabhu%2C%20Chheka%20Emmanuel%20and%20K%20Sojanya.%20Prabhu%2C%2040%2C%20a%20teacher%2C%20hails%20from%20Chennai%20and%20has%20been%20living%20in%20Sonbhadra%20since%202011%20after%20he%20came%20to%20a%20local%20church.%C2%A0%20Chekka%20Emmanuel%20and%20his%20wife%20K.%20Sojanya%20hail%20from%20Vijaywada%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20but%20have%20been%20residents%20of%20Sonbhadra%20for%20the%20past%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbjp-sikandar-bakht-love-jihad%5C%22%3EEven%20Sikandar%20Bakht%2C%20BJP%20Posterboy%20of%20Yesteryears%2C%20Would%20Know%20%E2%80%98Love%20Jihad%E2%80%99%20Is%20Only%20a%20Ruse%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20include%20pastors%20Sanjay%20John%2C%20Chotu%20Ranjan%2C%20Sohanram%20and%20Sant%20Lal%20Gond%2C%20Prakash%20HL%20Marandi%20(a%20teacher%20of%20St.%20Joseph%E2%80%99s%20school%20Shaktinagar%2C%20a%20co-educational%20English%20Medium%20School%2C%20established%20in%201978%2C%20and%20managed%20by%20the%20Roman%20Catholic%20Diocese%20of%20Allahabad%20Education%20Society)%2C%20sanitation%20workers%20Durgawati%20Devi%20and%20Parmanand%2C%20and%20priest%20Fr.%20Paras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20accused%20belong%20to%20the%20Dalit%2C%20OBC%20and%20tribal%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETripathi%20accused%20them%20of%20helping%20poor%20tribals%20financially%2C%20and%20distributing%20money%20and%20other%20essential%20items%20among%20them%20in%20order%20to%20get%20them%20converted%20to%20Christianity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20misled%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpoor%20and%20illiterate%20people%E2%80%9D%20by%20providing%20their%20children%20free%20education%2C%20free%20school%20uniforms%2C%20free%20books%20and%20do%20%3Cem%3Ejhaad%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%3Cem%3Ephoonk%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20style%20of%20exorcism)%20to%20cure%20them%20of%20ailments%20at%20%3Cem%3Echangai%20sabhas%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eheld%20every%20Sunday%2C%20he%20alleged%20in%20the%20FIR%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20is%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Tripathi%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20accused%20provided%20free%20treatment%20in%20Christian%20hospitals%20and%20while%20doing%20so%20gave%20the%20public%20from%20the%20tribal%20areas%20allurements%20to%20make%20them%20believe%20that%20%E2%80%9CJesus%20Christ%20is%20the%20only%20Eshwar%20(lord)%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CChristian%20faith%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20kalyan%20(welfare).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20such%20allurements%20and%20promises%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20(the%20people)%20are%20psychologically%20mesmerized%20towards%20conversion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonbhadra%20police%20ASP%20(headquarters)%20Kalu%20Singh%20said%20the%20natives%20of%20Southern%20states%20had%20been%20residing%20in%20Sonbhadra%20for%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20Nine%20out%20of%20the%2042%20had%20been%20arrested%20so%20far%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20claimed%20they%20had%20recovered%20over%20100%20religious%20items%20used%20by%20the%20accused%20to%20convert%20people.%20These%20included%2010%20copies%20of%20the%20Bible%2C%2013%20holy%20scriptures%2C%20307%20prayer%20pamphlets%2C%20five%20talking%20Bible%20audio%20tapes%2C%20a%20convention%20song%20CD%20and%20other%20prayer%20books%2C%20including%20one%20named%20%E2%80%98UP%20%3Cem%3Eke%20liye%20prarthana%20pushtak%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(A%20book%20of%20prayer%20for%20UP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20in%20Chopan%20area%2C%20the%20accused%20were%20spread%20across%20the%20district%2C%20which%20is%20known%20to%20be%20mineral-rich%20and%20shares%20a%20border%20with%20Jharkhand%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FZW9JxoJ6KOg%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Two%20Churches%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Targeted%20by%20Right%20Wing%20Group%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98What%20motive%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETripathi%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20unearthed%20a%20%E2%80%9Cweb%E2%80%9D%20of%20illegal%20conversion.%20While%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20was%20an%20office-bearer%20of%20the%20VHP%2C%20he%20said%20the%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20in%20his%20individual%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20motive%20did%20they%20have%20in%20coming%20to%20Sonbhadra%20all%20the%20way%20from%20Chennai%20and%20other%20southern%20states%3F%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20here%20for%20a%20job%20or%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20when%20asked%20why%20he%20accused%20Jai%20Prabhu%2C%20Emmanuel%20Chekka%20and%20K.%20Sojanya%20of%20illegal%20conversion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20bail%20applications%2C%20Prabhu%2C%20Emmanuel%20and%20four%20others%20said%20the%20allegations%20in%20the%20FIR%20against%20them%20were%20%E2%80%9Cbaseless%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cimaginary%E2%80%9D%20and%20accused%20the%20police%20of%20misusing%20the%20anti-conversion%20law.%20They%20argued%20that%20the%20complainant%20Tripathi%20nor%20his%20family%20nor%20anyone%20else%20had%20been%20converted%20by%20them.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20mention%20of%20anyone%20who%20was%20converted.%20The%20complainant%20considers%20himself%20thekadar%20of%20the%20dharm%C2%A0(contractor%20of%20the%20Hindu%20faith)%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20accused%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabhu%20and%20Emmanuel%20told%20the%20court%20they%20were%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESessions%20judge%2C%20Sonbhadra%2C%20Ashok%20Kumar%20Yadav%20granted%20them%20bail%2C%20observing%20that%20at%20this%20stage%20it%20did%20not%20appear%20that%20the%20accused%20converted%20people%20by%20force%20or%20against%20their%20wishes.%20It%20%E2%80%9Ccannot%20be%20said%20with%20certainty%E2%80%9D%20that%20they%20deceived%20people%20through%20inducements%20to%20leave%20their%20religion%20and%20adopt%20the%20Christian%20faith%2C%20judge%20Yadav%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20also%20commented%20on%20the%20religious%20material%20seized%20from%20the%20accused%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20not%20against%20the%20law%20for%20a%20person%20who%20followed%20a%20religion%20to%20have%20in%20his%20or%20her%20possession%20religious%20material%20related%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Free%20tuition%20classes%20in%20a%20Brahminical%20system%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20aide%20of%20the%20accused%20persons%2C%20speaking%20to%20The%20Wire%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20said%20the%20VHP%20activist%20had%20no%20%3Cem%3Elocus%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Estandi%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20lodging%20an%20FIR%20when%20those%20who%20were%20allegedly%20converted%20had%20not%20complained%20to%20the%20police.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20this%20means%20we%20have%20no%20right%20to%20even%20propagate%20our%20religion%3F%20People%20come%20to%20these%20sabhas%20on%20their%20own%20will.%20Nobody%20forces%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20feels%20the%20VHP%20targeted%20them%20because%20the%20sabhas%20were%20making%20SCs%20and%20STs%20in%20the%20area%20aware%20about%20their%20rights.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20main%20problem%20is%20that%20people%20should%20remain%20the%20way%20they%20were%2C%20that%20is%20under%20control%20of%20the%20Brahmanical%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20clarifying%20that%20those%20who%20attended%20these%20prayer%20meets%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20formally%20converted%20to%20Christianity%20and%20continue%20to%20follow%20their%20Hindu%20culture.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20follow%20their%20indigenous%20culture%20and%20Hindu%20faith%20but%20have%20Jesus%20in%20their%20hearts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdistributing-bibles-encouraging-childrens-education-not-allurement%5C%22%3EDistributing%20The%20Bible%2C%20Encouraging%20Education%20Not%20%E2%80%98Allurement%E2%80%99%20for%20Conversion%3A%20Allahabad%20HC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20as%20well%20as%20local%20police%20said%20that%20Prabhu%20and%20Emmanuel%2C%20who%20Tripathi%20has%20accused%20as%20being%20%E2%80%9Cringmasters%E2%80%9D%20of%20unlawful%20conversion%2C%20gave%20free%20tuition%20lessons%20to%20underprivileged%20children%20and%20helped%20their%20families%20with%20free%20medical%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESHO%20Chopan%C2%A0Vishwanath%20Pratap%20Singh%20said%20while%20nine%20persons%20were%20arrested%2C%20they%20were%20gathering%20more%20evidence%20against%20possible%20others%20of%20the%20others.%C2%A0%20Police%20were%20recording%20statements%20of%20%E2%80%9Cindependent%20witnesses%E2%80%9D%20who%20were%20allegedly%20converted%20at%20these%20meetings%20and%20gathering%20%E2%80%9Csupporting%20evidence%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20Tripathi%20in%20the%20FIR%2C%20Singh%20said.%20The%20accused%20had%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnetwork%20in%20the%20entire%20district%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatyajeet%20Gupta%2C%20SP%20of%20Sant%20Kabir%20Nagar%2C%20said%20a%20case%20had%20been%20registered%20at%20Khalilabad%20police%20station%20against%20Jose%20Pulluvelil%20and%20Elma%20Pulluvelil%2C%20who%20hail%20from%20Pathanamthitta%20district%20of%20Kerala%2C%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20one%20Nirmala%20Nishad%20who%20alleged%20that%20the%20accused%20had%20assured%20her%20that%20she%20would%20find%20her%20son%2C%20who%20was%20missing%20since%20three%20years%2C%20if%20she%20converted%20to%20Christianity.%20Nishad%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20accused%20used%20insulting%20language%20for%20Hindu%20deities%2C%20tore%20her%20kalava%20(religious%20threat%20worn%20on%20the%20wrist)%20and%20removed%20her%20mangalsutra%20and%20bichiya%20(toe%20ring).%20Nishad%20had%20alleged%20that%20the%20accused%20would%20induce%20people%20from%20Dalit%20communities%20to%20convert%20in%20the%20prarthna%20sabhas%20(prayer%20meetings)%20held%20in%20her%20village%20every%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGupta%20said%20the%20couple%20was%20sent%20to%20judicial%20custody%20after%20their%20statements%20were%20recorded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETextbook%20cases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sonbhadra%20case%2C%20though%20one%20among%20the%20hundreds%20of%20FIR%20lodged%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20UP%20under%20the%20anti-conversion%20law%20since%202020%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20textbook%20case%20of%20what%20a%20forceful%20conversion%20is%20in%20the%20eye%20of%20the%20state.%20In%20August%202021%2C%20seven%20months%20after%20the%20state%20government%20introduced%20a%20stringent%20new%20law%20against%20unlawful%20conversion%2C%20it%20submitted%20an%20affidavit%20in%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20providing%20two%20illustrations%20of%20%E2%80%9Cforced%20conversion%E2%80%9D%20in%20response%20to%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20constitutional%20validity%20of%20the%20law.%20One%20of%20the%20illustrations%20involved%20inter-faith%20marriages%20involving%20Hindu%20women.%20The%20second%20one%20was%20about%20Christian%20missionaries%20allegedly%20trying%20to%20convert%20Dalits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20talked%20about%20a%20group%20of%20Christian%20missionaries%20visiting%20a%20Dalit%20busty%20to%20allure%20every%20member%20of%20the%20community%20with%20the%20promise%20that%20if%20they%20started%20believing%20in%20God%20or%20started%20reading%20the%20Bible%2C%20they%20would%20be%20provided%20with%20a%20free%20training%20course%20as%20a%20nurse%20and%20later%20a%20job%20in%20a%20hospital.%20The%20missionaries%20allure%20them%20to%20leave%20their%20faith%20based%20on%20these%20assurances.%C2%A0The%20Dalits%20leaving%20their%20faith%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20these%20assurances%2C%C2%A0amounts%20to%20a%20forced%C2%A0conversion%2C%20the%20state%20government%20informed%20the%20HC.%20The%20Dalits%20in%20this%20case%20did%20not%20have%20a%20freedom%20of%20choice%20but%20their%20choice%20was%C2%A0obtained%20by%20certain%20allurement%2C%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702639802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15162605%2FUntitled-design.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Futtar-pradesh-police-religious-conversion-south-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20last%20two%20weeks%2C%20police%20in%20eastern%20UP%20have%20arrested%20at%20least%20four%20persons%20hailing%20from%20south%20Indian%20states%20on%20charges%20of%20allegedly%20trying%20to%20convert%20backward%20caste%20and%20tribal%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Futtar-pradesh-police-religious-conversion-south-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prince%20Harry%20wins%20damages%20over%20phone-hacking%20by%20British%20newspapers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702639305000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106022506%2Cimgsize-628263.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fprince-harry-wins-damages-over-phone-hacking-by-british-newspapers%2Farticleshow%2F106022320.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106022320.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPrince%20Harry%20awarded%20%C2%A3140%2C600%20after%20London's%20High%20Court%20ruled%20he%20was%20victim%20of%20phone%20hacking%20and%20unlawful%20information%20gathering%20by%20Mirror%20Group%20Newspapers.%20Harry%2C%20along%20with%20other%20claimants%2C%20took%20legal%20action%20over%20allegations%20of%20phone%20hacking%20and%20unlawful%20information%20gathering%20between%201991%20and%202011.%20The%20court%20found%20that%20Harry's%20phone%20was%20hacked%20to%20a%20modest%20extent.%20%26quot%3BWe%20welcome%20today's%20judgment%20that%20gives%20the%20business%20the%20necessary%20clarity%20to%20move%20forward%20from%20events%20that%20took%20place%20many%20years%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20MGN%20spokesperson%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fprince-harry-wins-damages-over-phone-hacking-by-british-newspapers%2Farticleshow%2F106022320.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fprince-harry-wins-damages-over-phone-hacking-by-british-newspapers%2Famp_articleshow%2F106022320.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fprince-harry-wins-damages-over-phone-hacking-by-british-newspapers%2Famp_articleshow%2F106022320.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hague%20court%20rejects%20bid%20to%20ban%20transfer%20to%20Israel%20of%20F-35%20fighter%20jet%20parts%20from%20Dutch%20warehouse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702638515000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106022317%2Cimgsize-879709.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fhague-court-rejects-bid-to-ban-transfer-to-israel-of-f-35-fighter-jet-parts-from-dutch-warehouse%2Farticleshow%2F106021848.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106021848.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20Dutch%20court%20rejects%20the%20request%20by%20human%20rights%20and%20humanitarian%20organizations%20to%20halt%20the%20transfer%20of%20F-35%20fighter%20jet%20parts%20to%20Israel.%20The%20court%20states%20that%20the%20Dutch%20government%20considered%20the%20relevant%20interests%20before%20agreeing%20to%20the%20delivery.%20The%20organizations%20argue%20that%20the%20transfer%20makes%20the%20Netherlands%20complicit%20in%20possible%20war%20crimes%20by%20Israel.%20The%20government's%20decision%20to%20continue%20the%20transfer%20despite%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20shows%20a%20prioritization%20of%20economic%20interests%20and%20diplomatic%20reputation%20over%20the%20laws%20of%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fhague-court-rejects-bid-to-ban-transfer-to-israel-of-f-35-fighter-jet-parts-from-dutch-warehouse%2Farticleshow%2F106021848.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fhague-court-rejects-bid-to-ban-transfer-to-israel-of-f-35-fighter-jet-parts-from-dutch-warehouse%2Famp_articleshow%2F106021848.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fhague-court-rejects-bid-to-ban-transfer-to-israel-of-f-35-fighter-jet-parts-from-dutch-warehouse%2Famp_articleshow%2F106021848.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Are%20the%20Unseen%20Effects%20of%20the%20Election%20Commissioner%20Bill%20on%20Electoral%20Governance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2012%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frajya-sabha-passes-bill-election-commissioners-opposition-appointment%5C%22%3Eapproved%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20Other%20Election%20Commissioners%20(Appointment%2C%20Conditions%20of%20Service%2C%20and%20Term%20of%20Office)%20Bill.%20This%20legislation%20replaces%20the%20Election%20Commission%20(Conditions%20of%20Service%20of%20Election%20Commissioners%20and%20Transaction%20of%20Business)%20Act%2C%201991.%20The%20primary%20objective%20of%20the%20Bill%20is%20to%20govern%20the%20appointment%2C%20terms%20of%20service%2C%20and%20tenure%20of%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20(CEC)%20and%20other%20Election%20Commissioners%20(ECs)%2C%20and%20to%20establish%20procedures%20for%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Bill%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20will%20be%20composed%20of%20a%20CEC%20and%20other%20ECs.%20The%20number%20of%20ECs%20will%20be%20determined%20periodically%20by%20the%20President.%20The%20appointment%20of%20the%20Commission%20will%20be%20made%20by%20the%20President%20based%20on%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Selection%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Committee%20consists%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20a%20cabinet%20minister%2C%20and%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20(or%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20single%20largest%20opposition%20party).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20minister%20will%20head%20a%20Search%20Committee%20tasked%20with%20proposing%20five%20names%20to%20the%20Selection%20Committee.%20Notably%2C%20the%20Selection%20Committee%20also%20holds%20the%20authority%20to%20consider%20individuals%20beyond%20those%20suggested%20by%20the%20Search%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20selection%20of%20the%20CEC%20and%20ECs%20under%20Article%20324%20is%20contingent%20upon%20legislation%20enacted%20by%20Parliament.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scobserver.in%2Fcases%2Fanoop-baranwal-v-union-of-india-election-commission-appointments-background%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAnoop%20Baranwal%20v%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20emphasised%20that%20the%20framers%20of%20the%20constitution%20intended%20to%20establish%20an%20independent%20Election%20Commission%20with%20appointments%20governed%20by%20law%2C%20not%20subject%20to%20executive%20discretion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20ruled%20that%2C%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20specific%20legislation%20from%20Parliament%2C%20the%20appointment%20of%20the%20CEC%20and%20ECs%20would%20be%20contingent%20on%20the%20recommendations%20of%20a%20Selection%20Committee.%20As%20per%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20vision%2C%20this%20Committee%20would%20comprise%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20and%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20(or%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20largest%20opposition%20party).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20current%20Bill%20raises%20concerns%20as%20it%20modifies%20this%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20negates%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20one%20cabinet%20minister%20is%20included%20in%20the%20Selection%20Committee.%20Consequently%2C%20the%20Selection%20Committee%20is%20predominantly%20composed%20of%20members%20from%20the%20ruling%20government%2C%20potentially%20jeopardising%20the%20independence%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Constituent%20Assembly%20members%20recognised%20the%20importance%20of%20entrusting%20the%20responsibility%20of%20conducting%20elections%20to%20individuals%20free%20from%20political%20influences%20and%20local%20pressures.%20Dr.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20emphasised%20that%20true%20electoral%20freedom%20required%20distancing%20elections%20from%20the%20control%20of%20the%20ruling%20government.%20Both%20the%20Goswami%20report%20of%201990%20and%20the%20Law%20Commission%20report%20of%202015%20specified%20that%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20should%20be%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Selection%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felection-commissioners-appointment-bill-farewell-to-free-and-fair-elections%5C%22%3EElection%20Commissioners%E2%80%99%20Appointment%20Bill%3A%20Farewell%20to%20Free%20and%20Fair%20Elections%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20limitations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20proposed%20Bill%2C%20only%20individuals%20who%20currently%20hold%20or%20have%20held%20a%20position%20equivalent%20to%20the%20secretary%20to%20the%20government%20are%20deemed%20eligible%20for%20the%20roles%20of%20CEC%20or%20ECs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20their%20administrative%20functions%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20also%20functions%20in%20a%20quasi-judicial%20capacity%2C%20making%20determinations%20on%20matters%20such%20as%20the%20disqualification%20of%20Members%20of%20Parliament%20and%20State%20Legislatures%2C%20as%20well%20as%20adjudicating%20disputes%20related%20to%20symbol%20allocation%20and%20the%20registration%20of%20political%20parties.%20The%20limitation%20of%20eligibility%20criteria%20to%20civil%20servants%20under%20the%20Bill%20raises%20concerns%20as%20it%20may%20exclude%20qualified%20individuals%20from%20diverse%20backgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComparatively%2C%20examining%20the%20composition%20of%20Election%20Commissions%20in%20other%20countries%20reveals%20a%20broader%20eligibility%20criteria.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20appointees%20must%20not%20be%20currently%20elected%20or%20appointed%20officers%2C%20nor%20hold%20federal%20government%20positions%20in%20the%20executive%2C%20legislative%2C%20or%20judicial%20branches%20at%20the%20time%20of%20their%20appointment.%20In%20South%20Africa%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20is%20a%20five-member%20body%2C%20with%20one%20member%20required%20to%20be%20a%20judge.%20All%20members%20must%20be%20South%20African%20citizens%20without%20prominent%20party-political%20affiliations.%20This%20highlights%20a%20more%20inclusive%20approach%20to%20eligibility%20in%20other%20countries%E2%80%99%20electoral%20bodies%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20more%20restrictive%20criteria%20proposed%20by%20the%20current%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20affirms%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20Selection%20Committee%20even%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20vacancy%20or%20an%20issue%20in%20its%20constitution.%20However%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20note%20that%20a%20vacancy%20in%20this%20Committee%20can%20only%20occur%20under%20specific%20circumstances.%20Among%20the%20three%20Committee%20members%2C%20the%20positions%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20are%20inherently%20secure%20and%20cannot%20be%20vacant.%20The%20only%20potential%20vacancy%20could%20be%20in%20the%20position%20of%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20which%20may%20arise%20if%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20dissolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20a%20vacancy%20may%20only%20occur%20before%20a%20general%20election%2C%20and%20during%20such%20a%20period%2C%20the%20Selection%20Committee%20would%20exclusively%20comprise%20members%20from%20the%20ruling%20party.%20This%20scenario%20raises%20concerns%20about%20the%20potential%20lack%20of%20opposition%20representation%20in%20the%20Selection%20Committee%20during%20crucial%20decision-making%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20Bill%20neglects%20to%20address%20persistent%20issues%20that%20have%20plagued%20the%20Election%20Commission%20over%20the%20years.%20Notably%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20recognise%20that%20no%20CEC%20has%20successfully%20completed%20a%20full%20six-year%20term%20since%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinancial%20matters%20concerning%20the%20Election%20Commission%20are%20subject%20to%20government%20control%2C%20with%20the%20funds%20not%20being%20drawn%20from%20the%20consolidated%20fund%20of%20India.%20This%20arrangement%20implies%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20wields%20significant%20power%20and%20authority%20over%20the%20finances%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20lacks%20an%20independent%20staff%2C%20relying%20on%20personnel%20from%20both%20central%20and%20state%20governments%20whenever%20elections%20are%20conducted.%20In%20essence%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20operates%20as%20a%20largely%20powerless%20entity%2C%20as%20it%20lacks%20the%20ability%20to%20enforce%20inner-party%20democracy%20or%20regulate%20party%20finances.%20These%20shortcomings%20underscore%20the%20need%20for%20comprehensive%20reforms%20that%20go%20beyond%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20current%20Bill%20in%20order%20to%20address%20the%20systemic%20challenges%20faced%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20overlooked%20the%20private%20member%20Bill%20presented%20by%20MP%20Manish%20Tewari%2C%20which%20purportedly%20contained%20solutions%20to%20the%20existing%20problems%20within%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20The%20Bill%20argued%20that%20the%20internal%20structures%20and%20functioning%20of%20numerous%20political%20parties%20had%20become%20excessively%20opaque%20and%20rigid%2C%20emphasising%20the%20necessity%20to%20make%20their%20operations%20transparent%2C%20accountable%2C%20and%20rule-based.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20envisioned%20Selection%20Committee%20in%20the%20Bill%20included%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20as%20the%20chairman%2C%20alongside%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20the%20two%20most%20senior%20judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20as%20its%20members.%20This%20proposed%20committee%20aimed%20to%20bring%20a%20more%20inclusive%20and%20diverse%20approach%20to%20the%20decision-making%20process%20regarding%20the%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20structure%20and%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20also%20proposed%20that%20the%20regulation%2C%20monitoring%20and%20superintendence%20of%20internal%20functioning%20including%20but%20not%20limited%20to%20internal%20election%20of%20all%20registered%20political%20parties%20under%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%2C%201951%20shall%20be%20vested%20in%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20further%20said%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20shall%20regulate%2C%20monitor%20and%20superintend%20the%20internal%20election%20of%20registered%20political%20parties%20in%20accordance%20with%20their%20respective%20constitutions%20until%20a%20Model%20Internal%20Code%20is%20prescribed%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suggested%20alterations%20could%20potentially%20impact%20the%20autonomy%20and%20operations%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20.%20The%20independence%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20is%20paramount%20to%20guarantee%20impartiality%20and%20integrity%20in%20the%20execution%20of%20electoral%20processes.%20Any%20perceived%20influence%20of%20the%20Executive%20in%20the%20selection%20process%20may%20give%20rise%20to%20apprehensions%20regarding%20the%20EC%E2%80%99s%20capacity%20to%20fulfil%20its%20duties%20without%20prejudice.%20Upholding%20the%20non-partisan%20nature%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20is%20essential%20for%20maintaining%20public%20trust%20in%20the%20electoral%20system%20and%20ensuring%20fair%20and%20unbiased%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBhuvnesh%20Kumar%20and%20Sharad%20Panwar%20are%20fourth%20year%20law%20students%20at%20the%20National%20Law%20University%2C%20Jodhpur.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702638005000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhat-are-the-unseen-effects-of-the-election-commissioner-bill-on-electoral-governance%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Any%20perceived%20influence%20of%20the%20Executive%20in%20the%20selection%20process%20of%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20Other%20Election%20Commissioners%20may%20give%20rise%20to%20apprehensions%20regarding%20the%20Election%20Commission's%20capacity%20to%20fulfil%20its%20duties%20without%20prejudice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhat-are-the-unseen-effects-of-the-election-commissioner-bill-on-electoral-governance%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20presses%20Gaza%20assault%20as%20top%20US%20official%20visits%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702637911000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106021919%2Cimgsize-1470082.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-presses-gaza-assault-as-top-us-official-visits%2Farticleshow%2F106021538.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106021538.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIsrael%20pressed%20its%20offensive%20in%20Gaza%20on%20Friday%20despite%20mounting%20international%20calls%20for%20restraint%2C%20with%20key%20backer%20the%20United%20States%20saying%20the%20war%20to%20crush%20Hamas%20must%20not%20lead%20to%20a%20long-term%20Israeli%20occupation%20of%20the%20territory.%20The%20United%20States%2C%20which%20provides%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20military%20aid%20to%20Israel%2C%20has%20strongly%20backed%20its%20response%20to%20Hamas's%20attacks%2C%20but%20has%20voiced%20increasing%20concern%20over%20civilian%20casualties%20and%20the%20long-term%20plan%20for%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-presses-gaza-assault-as-top-us-official-visits%2Farticleshow%2F106021538.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-presses-gaza-assault-as-top-us-official-visits%2Famp_articleshow%2F106021538.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-presses-gaza-assault-as-top-us-official-visits%2Famp_articleshow%2F106021538.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Poland%20to%20get%20first%205%20billion%20euros%20in%20EU%20funds%20this%20year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702636703000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106020971%2Cimgsize-25288.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fpoland-to-get-first-5-billion-euros-in-eu-funds-this-year%2Farticleshow%2F106020936.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106020936.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EEU%20to%20transfer%205%20billion%20euros%20to%20Poland%20to%20aid%20energy%20transition%20away%20from%20fossil%20fuels%20and%20support%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%20The%20first%20transfer%20of%20funds%20is%20part%20of%20a%20program%20that%20is%20free%20from%20the%20usual%20rule%20of%20law%20conditions.%20More%20money%20will%20come%20as%20Poland%20restores%20an%20independent%20judiciary.%20Poland's%20new%20prime%20minister%2C%20Donald%20Tusk%2C%20vows%20to%20prioritize%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20aims%20to%20join%20the%20EU's%20European%20Public%20Prosecutor's%20Office.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fpoland-to-get-first-5-billion-euros-in-eu-funds-this-year%2Farticleshow%2F106020936.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fpoland-to-get-first-5-billion-euros-in-eu-funds-this-year%2Famp_articleshow%2F106020936.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fpoland-to-get-first-5-billion-euros-in-eu-funds-this-year%2Famp_articleshow%2F106020936.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Union%20Govt%20Tells%20SC%20it%20Will%20Follow%20CBI%20Manual%20on%20Device%20Seizure.%20Here's%20What%20the%20Manual%20Says.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15141230%2Feirik-solheim-mWTOR3Rx8l8-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20government%20on%20Thursday%20sought%20yet%20another%20adjournment%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20hearing%20petitions%20on%20device%20seizures%2C%20on%20the%20excuse%20that%20its%20committee%20was%20still%20discussing%20suitable%20guidelines%20on%20the%20search%20and%20seizure%20of%20phones%20and%20other%20electronic%20devices.%20Even%20as%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20orally%20expressed%20discomfort%20at%20the%20repeated%20adjournments%20sought%20by%20the%20government%2C%20it%20recorded%20the%20statement%20of%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20S.V.%20Raju%2C%20representing%20the%20government%2C%20that%20the%20Union%20agencies%20will%20strictly%20adhere%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20Manual%202020%20on%20search%20and%20seizure%20in%20the%20meantime%2C%20while%20giving%20government%20a%20further%20time%20of%20six%20weeks%20to%20finalise%20the%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Sanjay%20Kishan%20Kaul%2C%20who%20is%20about%20to%20demit%20office%20later%20this%20month%2C%20and%20Justice%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20was%20hearing%20a%20batch%20of%20writ%20petitions%20including%20one%20brought%20by%20well-known%20academics%20Ram%20Ramaswamy%2C%20Sujata%20Patel%2C%20M.%20Madhava%20Prasad%2C%20Mukul%20Kesavan%20and%20Deepak%20Malghan%2C%20represented%20by%20senior%20advocate%20Nitya%20Ramakrishnan%2C%20and%20another%20brought%20by%20Foundation%20for%20Media%20Professionals%2C%20represented%20by%20senior%20advocate%20Siddharth%20Agrawal.%20The%20matter%20is%20set%20to%20come%20up%20next%20for%20hearing%20on%20February%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20since%20had%20a%20chance%20to%20review%20some%20of%20the%20guidelines%20proposed%20as%20interim%20guidelines%20by%20the%20petitioners%20in%20the%20case%20and%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20CBI%20Manual%2C%202020%2C%20which%20bears%20a%20%E2%80%98Restricted%E2%80%99%20classification%20label.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigating%20agencies%20will%20now%20have%20to%20observe%20procedures%20such%20as%20generation%20of%20hash%20value%20for%20each%20device%20at%20the%20time%20of%20seizure%20of%20such%20devices%2C%20to%20be%20recorded%20in%20the%20seizure%20memo.%20For%20instance%2C%20one%20of%20the%20guidelines%20suggested%20by%20the%20petitioners%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3E%5Bt%5Dhe%20chain%20of%20custody%20of%20the%20material%20must%20be%20maintained%2C%20and%20the%20hash%20values%20of%20the%20devices%20must%20be%20recorded%20and%20verified%20at%20each%20transition.%20Each%20step%20must%20be%20documented%20and%20explained%20so%20that%20a%20third%20party%20should%20be%20able%20to%20replicate%20the%20process%20and%20arrive%20at%20the%20same%20result.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20requirement%20is%20provided%20for%20under%20the%20manual%20detailing%20procedures%20of%20hash%20value%20generation%20at%20the%20time%20of%20seizure%2C%20recording%20of%20the%20same%20in%20the%20seizure%20memo%2C%20the%20opening%20of%20chain%20of%20custody%20reports%20at%20the%20time%20of%20seizure%2C%20and%20the%20hash%20value%20and%20the%20chain%20of%20custody%20reports%20being%20made%20available%20along%20with%20the%20devices%20to%20the%20forensic%20laboratory%20(Sections%2016.19%20and%2016.23).%20The%20importance%20attached%20to%20the%20chain%20of%20custody%20is%20underlined%20in%20Section%2012.24%20where%20it%20says%20%E2%80%9C%5Bi%3Cem%3E%5Df%20it%20is%20not%20properly%20maintained%2C%20an%20item%20may%20become%20inadmissible%20in%20the%20court.%20Failure%20to%20substantiate%20the%20chain%20of%20custody%20may%20lead%20to%20serious%20questions%20regarding%20the%20authenticity%20and%20integrity%20of%20the%20evidence%20and%20the%20examination%20rendered%20upon%20it%2C%20making%20the%20whole%20process%20as%20an%20exercise%20in%20futility.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20consistent%20with%20the%20petitioners%E2%80%99%20suggestion%20that%20the%20evidence%20obtained%20without%20scrupulously%20following%20these%20safeguards%20to%20ordinarily%20not%20be%20admitted%20against%20any%20person%20accused%20of%20an%20offence%20in%20criminal%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20provision%20in%20the%20manual%20is%20the%20requirement%20of%20the%20investigating%20agency%20to%20avoid%20indiscriminate%20seizure.%20Section%209.12%20of%20the%20manual%20states%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%3Cem%3Ethere%20should%20be%20no%20indiscriminate%20seizure%20of%20documents%20in%20any%20case.%20It%20should%20be%20borne%20in%20mind%20that%20seizure%20of%20records%20may%20cause%20dislocation%20of%20work%20in%20the%20office%20concerned.%20Hence%2C%20records%20should%20not%20be%20taken%20into%20possession%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20routine.%20The%20IO%20should%20seize%2Frequisition%20the%20records%20only%20if%20the%20same%20are%20essential%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20investigation.%20In%20many%20cases%2C%20examination%20and%20scrutiny%20of%20the%20records%20on%20the%20spot%20might%20suffice%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%20Petitioners%20have%20suggested%20that%20no%20seizure%20or%20search%20of%20personal%20digital%20device%20be%20effected%20without%20a%20judicial%20warrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20this%20was%20mentioned%20in%20court%20on%20Thursday%2C%20ASG%20Raju%20expressed%20a%20severe%20disagreement%20and%20spoke%20of%20leakages%20as%20though%20the%20requirement%20of%20a%20search%20warrant%20was%20inimical%20to%20law%20enforcement.%20He%20was%20perhaps%2C%20unmindful%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20CBI%20Manual%20itself%20makes%20obtainment%20of%20a%20judicial%20warrant%20%E2%80%98preferable%E2%80%99%20before%20search.%20If%20it%20is%20to%20be%20followed%2C%20the%20agency%20would%20presumably%20have%20to%20justify%20any%20breach%20of%20the%20preferred%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20other%20key%20demands%20of%20the%20petitioners%20remain%20unmet%20by%20the%20CBI%20Manual.%20The%20Manual%20also%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20have%20any%20safeguards%20relating%20to%20passwords%2Fcredentials%20coercion%2C%20and%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20device%20owner%20during%20examination%20of%20the%20devices%20or%20data%2C%20and%20the%20need%20for%20segregation%20privileged%20material%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20journalistic%20material%2C%20privileged%20correspondence%20such%20as%20between%20an%20attorney%20and%20a%20client%2C%20or%20a%20doctor%20and%20a%20patient%2C%20communications%20between%20spouses%20as%20also%20all%20irrelevant%20and%20personal%20material.%20Other%20than%20deprecating%20any%20%E2%80%9Cindiscriminate%20seizure%20of%20documents%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20CBI%20Manual%20does%20not%20make%20any%20provision%20to%20ensure%20that%20this%20is%20not%20done.%20Yet%2C%20agencies%20must%20now%20be%20mindful%20of%20this%20principle%2C%20which%20they%20have%20all%20along%20been%20ignoring%20till%20date%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20of%20the%20petitioners%E2%80%99%20asks%20is%20a%20definitive%20guideline%20on%20timelines%20for%20return%20of%20digital%20devices%2C%20and%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20be%20addressed%20in%20the%20CBI%20Manual%2C%20although%20it%20has%20a%20general%20directive%20for%20expeditious%20return%20of%20seized%20material%20(whether%20digital%20or%20otherwise)%20in%20Section%209.16.%20However%2C%20this%20concern%20may%20somewhat%20be%20mitigated%20by%20the%20mandate%20under%20Section%209.41%20that%20investigation%20should%20be%20carried%20out%20only%20on%20the%20mirror%20image%20of%20the%20data%20obtained%20from%20the%20devices%20%E2%80%93%20thereby%20obviating%20the%20need%20for%20the%20investigation%20agencies%20to%20retain%20the%20devices%20after%20the%20mirroring%20process%20is%20complete.%C2%A0%20It%20may%20also%20be%20noted%20that%20Section%209.16%20of%20the%20Manual%20lays%20down%20an%20outer%20limit%20of%20a%20fortnight%20for%20the%20preparation%20of%20the%20CBI%20report%20and%20mandate%20the%20obtaining%20of%20orders%20from%20the%20magistrate%20under%20Section%20457%20of%20the%20CrPC%20for%20disposal%20or%20return%20of%20seized%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20this%2C%20Thursday%E2%80%99s%20order%20of%20the%20court%20is%20certainly%20a%20step%20forward%20in%20bringing%20some%20discipline%20to%20investigation%20practices%20around%20search%20and%20seizure%20of%20personal%20digital%20devices.%C2%A0%20Investigating%20agencies%20are%20not%20known%20to%20observe%20many%20of%20these%20safeguards.%20Reportage%20on%20the%20recent%20cases%20involving%20the%20founding%20editors%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdevice-journalists-seized-press-freedom-delhi-court-the-wire%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20journalists%20associated%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fweeks-after-unprecedented-raids-newsclick-staffers-grapple-with-waiting-game%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20stands%20testament%20to%20this.%20For%20instance%2C%20neither%20were%20hash%20value%20reports%20provided%20at%20the%20time%20of%20seizure%2C%20nor%20were%20the%20devices%20returned%20in%20a%20timely%20manner%20to%20the%20device%20owners.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702636226000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15141230%2Feirik-solheim-mWTOR3Rx8l8-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Funion-govt-tells-sc-it-will-follow-cbi-manual-on-device-seizure-heres-what-the-manual-says%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20has%20promised%20to%20follow%20the%20CBI%20Manual%20while%20it%20works%20on%20preparing%20guidelines.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Funion-govt-tells-sc-it-will-follow-cbi-manual-on-device-seizure-heres-what-the-manual-says%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anger%20over%20sentencing%20of%20boy%2C%2010%2