E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%C2%A0a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%C2%A0The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3Eclick%20here%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20stark%20geopolitical%20tensions%20which%20have%20become%20characteristic%20of%20international%20summits%20lately%2C%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20global%20climate%20conference%20COP28%20witnessed%20sharper%20differences%20between%20the%20%E2%80%98Like%20Minded%20Developing%20Countries%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20and%20the%20developed%20countries%20of%20the%20Global%20North.%20After%20the%20final%20day%20(December%2012)%20of%20the%20two-week%20COP28%20climate%20summit%20in%20Dubai%20saw%20a%20stalemate%20over%20the%20draft%20agreement%2C%20representatives%20continued%20negotiations%20to%20finally%20arrive%20at%20what%20is%20clearly%20now%20a%20compromised%20consensus%2C%20with%20terms%20like%20%E2%80%98unambitious%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98incremental%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98menu%E2%80%99%20and%20of%20%E2%80%98half%20measures%E2%80%99%20being%20used%20to%20describe%20the%20final%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F4821425d-d54b-411b-b48b-156005a5311f%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F4821425d-d54b-411b-b48b-156005a5311f%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1702714281336000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2V6o4xsd9yZ-BCQp_Mh-ZM%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edraft%20presented%20by%20COP28%20President%2C%20UAE%E2%80%99s%20Sultan%20al-Jaber%3C%2Fa%3E%20proposed%20eight%20options%20that%20countries%20could%20use%20to%20cut%20emissions%2C%20including%3A%20%E2%80%9Creducing%20both%20consumption%20and%20production%20of%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20in%20a%20just%2C%20orderly%20and%20equitable%20manner%20so%20as%20to%20achieve%20net%20zero%20by%2C%20before%2C%20or%20around%202050%E2%80%9D%2C%20falling%20short%20of%20referring%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Cphase%20out%E2%80%9D%20of%20fossil%20fuels.%20It%20included%20tripling%20renewable%20energy%20capacity%20by%202030%2C%20%E2%80%9Crapidly%20phasing%20down%20unabated%20coal%E2%80%9D%20and%20scaling%20up%20technologies%20including%20those%20to%20capture%20CO2%20emissions%20to%20keep%20them%20from%20the%20atmosphere.%20The%20US%2C%20UK%20and%20EU%20led%20more%20than%20a%20hundred%20countries%20to%20oppose%20the%20draft%20agreement%20which%20mentions%20the%20need%20to%20reduce%20emissions%20but%20did%20not%20outrightly%20state%20that%20fossil%20fuels%20should%20be%20phased%20out.%20Representatives%20for%20smaller%20Island%20Nations%20called%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdeath%20sentence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20deal%20now%20calls%20for%20%E2%80%9Ctransitioning%20away%20from%20fossil%20fuels%20in%20energy%20systems%2C%20in%20a%20just%2C%20orderly%20and%20equitable%20manner%20%E2%80%A6%20so%20as%20to%20achieve%20net%20zero%20by%202050%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20science%2C%E2%80%9D%20dropping%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9Cphasing%20away%E2%80%9D%20and%20including%20%E2%80%9Cfossil%20fuel.%E2%80%9D%20The%20agreement%20further%20calls%20for%20phasing%20out%20inefficient%20fossil%20fuel%20subsidies%20and%20for%20%E2%80%9Caccelerating%20phase%20down%E2%80%9D%20of%20coal%20usage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20developing%20nations%20along%20with%20major%20oil%20producers%20are%20opposed%20to%20any%20demand%20for%20phasing%20out%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20the%20point%20that%20India%20had%20been%20making%20throughout%20the%20discussions%20is%20that%20the%20focus%20needs%20to%20move%20away%20from%20coal%20because%20the%20science%20very%20clearly%20states%20that%20it%20is%20a%20carbon%20emission%20problem%20and%20all%20the%20fossil%20fuels%20need%20to%20be%20targeted.%20Although%20the%20discussions%20failed%20to%20feature%20accountability%20for%20historic%20polluters%2C%20in%20his%20speech%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F03336eaa-d80b-4b11-8f01-9b59e34dfdde%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F03336eaa-d80b-4b11-8f01-9b59e34dfdde%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1702714281336000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0CjTLS6pxrxuek3cs8cqM2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20%E2%80%9Crebuked%E2%80%9D%20large%20emitters%20like%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20releasing%20the%20most%20climate-warming%20emissions%20since%20the%20Industrial%20Revolution%20at%20COP28%2C%20%E2%80%9COver%20the%20past%20century%2C%20a%20small%20section%20of%20humanity%20has%20indiscriminately%20exploited%20nature.%20However%2C%20entire%20humanity%20is%20paying%20the%20price%20for%20this%2C%20especially%20people%20living%20in%20the%20Global%20South.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exclusive%20focus%20on%20%E2%80%98rapidly%20phasing%20down%20coal%E2%80%99%20drew%20exception%20from%20India%2C%20and%20it%20was%20joined%20by%20China%20in%20abstaining%20from%20signing%20the%20Global%20Renewables%20and%20Energy%20Efficiency%20Pledge%20aimed%20at%20tripling%20installed%20renewable%20energy%20capacity%20by%202030.%20Despite%20finding%20mention%20at%20the%20G20%20declaration%20in%20September%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20not%20sign%20the%20COP28%20global%20pledge%20was%20likely%20related%20to%20the%20framing%20of%20the%20text%20specifically%20around%20the%20severe%20stance%20on%20phasing%20out%20coal.%20India%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20phasing%20in%20renewables%2C%20and%20upholds%20that%20tripling%20of%20renewable%20energy%20and%20doubling%20of%20energy%20efficiency%20must%20not%20be%20covered%20with%20the%20phasing%20out%20of%20coal.%20As%20part%20of%20its%20nationally%20determined%20contributions%20(NDCs)%2C%20it%20has%20already%20committed%20to%20installing%20500%20GW%20of%20electricity%20from%20non-fossil%20fuel%20sources%20by%202030.%20Between%202017-23%2C%20India%20added%20100%20GW%20of%20installed%20electric%20capacity%2C%20of%20which%2080%25%20was%20from%20renewable%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20coal%E2%80%99s%20days%20are%20not%20over%20in%20India.%20Despite%20setting%20out%20some%20of%20the%20most%20aggressive%20renewable%20energy%20targets%20in%20the%20world%2C%20coal%20remains%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20urban%20industrial%20development%20projects%2C%20and%20a%20major%20source%20of%20jobs.%20It%20is%20important%20for%20the%20Global%20North%20to%20appreciate%20what%20transition%20from%20coal%20means%20for%20poor%20countries%20like%20India.%20Just%20consider%20the%20coal%20supply%20chains%2C%20taking%20India%20as%20a%20typical%20country%20of%20the%20global%20South.%20From%20the%20pitheads%2C%20coal%20is%20brought%20by%20trucks%20to%20a%20nearby%20cold%20depot%20from%20where%20it%20is%20transported%20again%20by%20trucks%20to%20the%20nearest%20railway%20station.%20Truck%20driving%20is%20the%20profession%20of%20choice%20for%20many%20poor%20migrants%20from%20rural%20areas%20and%20there%20are%20some%20two%20million%20registered%20on%20Indian%20roads.%20By%20a%20conservative%20estimate%2C%20at%20least%20a%20quarter%20of%20this%20carries%20coal.%20Each%20truck%20has%20a%20driver%20and%20two%20helpers%20who%20have%20families%2C%20which%20means%20that%201.5%20million%20are%20reliant%20on%20just%20coal%20trucking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupply%20chain%20disruptions%20due%20to%20developments%20in%20Ukraine%20have%20slowed%20down%20the%20momentum%20in%20transitioning%20to%20renewable%20energy%20options%2C%20everywhere.%20Upgrades%20for%20electricity%20storage%20require%20large%20tracts%20of%20land%20and%20transmission%20systems%20are%20built%20for%20coal%20and%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20which%20means%20they%20will%20need%20significant%20technology%20advancement%20for%20renewables.%20Nuclear%20and%20hydropower%20are%20considered%20essential%20to%20energy%20transitions%2C%20but%20globally%20there%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fefad627c-f556-4bc1-9291-5b98b45c0065%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fefad627c-f556-4bc1-9291-5b98b45c0065%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1702714281336000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0-eLIT0ohMR3JVRdEGMYMx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20disagreement%20over%20whether%20large%20dams%20are%20within%20the%20purview%20of%20renewable%20energy%20sources%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommitments%20made%20around%20climate%20finance%20at%20COP28%20remain%20weak%2C%20and%20although%20a%20%24700%20million%20loss%20and%20damage%20fund%20has%20been%20approved%2C%20it%20falls%20way%20below%20the%20estimated%20%24400%20billion%20needed%20to%20effectively%20begin%20addressing%20climate%20change.%20Technology%20transfers%20have%20been%20spoken%20of%20at%20COP28%3B%20but%20how%20much%20of%20this%20will%20actually%20transpire%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20The%20developed%20world%20retains%20its%20significant%20representation%20in%20deciding%20where%20funds%20go.%20Without%20financial%20backing%2C%20developing%20nations%20cannot%20think%20of%20ambitious%20action%20on%20mitigations.%20Sustainable%20finance%20instruments%20and%20technology%20transfer%20remain%20critical%20to%20building%20expensive%20projects%20that%20can%20effectively%20address%20climate%20change.%20The%20nature%20of%20finance%20flows%20needs%20to%20be%20demystified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20must%20insist%20that%20the%20fossil%20fuel%20phase-out%20must%20be%20differentiated%20depending%20on%20national%20circumstances%20and%20on%20a%20time%20scale%2C%20and%20technology%20transfer%2C%20co-development%20and%20access%20form%20the%20core%20of%20the%20energy%20transition.%20The%20COP28%20Dubai%20agreement%20may%20have%20created%20optics%20of%20convergence%20between%20the%20developed%20and%20developing%20countries%2C%20but%20there%20will%20be%20massive%20dissonance%20over%20how%20differentiated%20responsibility%20will%20be%20worked%20out%20in%20determining%20the%20absolute%20reduction%20of%20emissions%20over%20the%20next%20decade%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVaishali%20Basu%20Sharma%20is%20a%20strategic%20and%20economic%20affairs%20analyst.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702630835000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15140054%2FGBNy-spXEAA_v-G.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcop28-floundered-fossil-fuels-coal-finance%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20must%20insist%20that%20the%20fossil%20fuel%20phase-out%20must%20be%20differentiated%20depending%20on%20national%20circumstances%20and%20on%20a%20time%20scale%2C%20and%20technology%20transfer%2C%20co-development%20and%20access%20form%20the%20core%20of%20the%20energy%20transition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcop28-floundered-fossil-fuels-coal-finance%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I%20apologize%20for%20this'%3A%20Why%20Putin%20said%20sorry%20to%20Russians%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702629366000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-1060