20whole%20new%20audience%20to%20Moko%E2%80%99s%20music%20and%20provided%20some%20interesting%20insights%20into%20what%20is%20going%20on%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Ftopics%2Fnagaland%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENagaland%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20on%20the%20subject%20of%20prohibition.%20In%20the%20song%2C%20for%20example%2C%20Moko%20reflects%20on%20how%20alcohol%20is%20prohibited%20in%20Nagaland%20but%20everyone%20knows%20where%20to%20find%20it%20and%20how%20that%20illegal%20liquor%20comes%20from%20Assam%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20local%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20really%20wanted%20to%20address%20the%20hypocrisy%20behind%20alcohol%20prohibition%20in%20Nagaland.%20Many%20in%20Nagaland%20are%20asking%20for%20prohibition%20to%20be%20lifted%2C%20but%20the%20church%20and%20other%20civil%20society%20groups%20are%20coming%20in%20strong%20to%20oppose%20it.%20Ironically%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20the%20sons%20of%20church%20members%20getting%20drunk%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20funny%20thing%20is%20that%20the%20song%20has%20anti-government%20undertones%2C%20but%20at%20certain%20functions%20where%20I%20performed%20the%20song%20in%20front%20of%20government%20officials%2C%20they%20seemed%20to%20enjoy%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20song%20also%20makes%20clear%20references%20to%20the%20pride%20Moko%20feels%20in%20his%20Naga%20identity%20and%20the%20prejudices%20that%20people%20in%20mainland%20Indians%20harbour%20against%20Nagas%2C%20including%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F273338%2Fengineer-quits-job-pickle-business-nagaland-nitu-viluo-bengaluru%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efood%20habits%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBahar%20mannu%20ki%20ki%20kobi%20etu%20moi%20najane%20(Let%20people%20judge%20us%20because%